NK102(ne)004:1: // sbas pa'i rgum chung gi tshig 'grel /
NK102(ne)004:3: zhes nyon mongs pa'i bdun bcom pas /
NK102(ne)004:9: bcas pa'i bag chags dang yongs su bral ba /
NK102(ne)004:11: gdos bcas sha khrag gi phung po gnas 'gyur te
NK102(ne)004:12: 'ja' lus 'od phung mtshan dpe'i dkyil 'khor du 'gyur
NK102(ne)004:13: ba / lha'i bu'i bdud bcom pas /
NK102(ne)004:14: chos nyid la mnyam par bzhag pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:15: kun tu rtog pa'i rjes thob gnyis su med pa mnyam rjes ris med du 'gyur ba /
NK102(ne)004:17: skye 'chi las yongs su 'das te zag med rdo rje'i sku mchog brnyes pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:19: ces ye gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems su
NK102(ne)004:20: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis su ma grub na'ang
NK102(ne)004:21: / de'i rang gdangs ma 'gags pa'i rtsal sna tshogs
NK102(ne)004:22: su shar ba de nyid rang du rig pas rang
NK102(ne)004:24: dus kun tu 'khrul ma myong ba'i ye shes kyi
NK102(ne)004:25: rol pa zang thal bzang po'i ngang nyid du la
NK102(ne)004:26: 'das par kun tu bzang po'am thog ma'i sangs rgyas
NK102(ne)004:27: su grags shing / ye gzhi de rang ma rig pa las sems can du 'khrul pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:28: rang snang 'khrul pas gzhan du bzung ba ni ji
NK102(ne)004:29: ltar d+ha tu ra zos pas snang ba sna tshogs
NK102(ne)004:30: su snang ba dang 'dra ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:31: ye gzhi gcig las gnyis su 'byung ba ni dpe dug dang mtshungs pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:32: dug de shes na sman du 'gyur zhing nad sel bar byed la /
NK102(ne)004:33: ma shes na tshe'i dus byed pa'i dug yin pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:34: ye gzhi de ka rig na sangs rgyas yin la /
NK102(ne)004:35: ma rig na sems can te ye gzhi gcig las
NK102(ne)004:36: sangs rgyas dang sems can dus mnyam du byung zhing
NK102(ne)004:37: / kun tu bzang pos 'khor ba'i ming tsam yang
NK102(ne)004:38: ma grags par rang thog tu rang ngo shes pas
NK102(ne)004:39: / grol ba dang / de'i gong du sangs rgyas gzhan ma byung bas thog ma'i sangs rgyas sam /
NK102(ne)004:40: dang po'i sangs rgyas zhes su grags pa /
NK102(ne)004:41: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi sngon rol tu nyid byang chub pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:42: tshogs gnyis la ma bsten pa'i sangs rgyas mi srid pa'ang mi bsam ste /
NK102(ne)004:43: de ni thog ma'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po yin la /
NK102(ne)004:44: de'i gong du sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi tha
NK102(ne)004:45: snyad tsam yang med na tshogs gnyis zhes bya ba
NK102(ne)004:47: de 'dra'i grol ba thob pa de ni ye gzhi'i
NK102(ne)004:48: gnas lugs ji ltar yin pa la yin par rtogs
NK102(ne)004:49: pa'i don gyis nyid byang chub pa las /
NK102(ne)004:50: tshogs gnyis kyi mthus nyid byang chub pa zhig ma yin /
NK102(ne)004:51: tshogs gnyis bsags pa de ni sgrib pa gnyis sbyang ba'i ched du yin la /
NK102(ne)004:52: sgrib pa gnyis ni gnyis 'dzin gyi bag chags brtas
NK102(ne)004:53: pa las 'byung dgos pa'i tshul rnams kun tu bzang
NK102(ne)004:54: po'i dgongs pa zang thal du bstan pa'i rgyud le'u
NK102(ne)004:55: dgu pa las gsal bar gsungs pa de yin /
NK102(ne)004:57: zhes sbyang bya gzhi dus kyi skye 'chi bar do
NK102(ne)004:58: gsum po de dag sbyong byed sku gsum gyi lam
NK102(ne)004:59: khyer bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis sgo gsum tha mal gyi
NK102(ne)004:60: snang zhen las ldog pa'i gsang sngags bla med kyi
NK102(ne)004:61: sgyur lam bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:62: bskyed rim gyi myong ba thon pa'i gang zag gis
NK102(ne)004:63: rang gi lus rdo rje'i phung po'i rtsa rlung thig
NK102(ne)004:64: le rnams la gnad du bsnun te bsgoms pa'i stobs
NK102(ne)004:65: kyis las rlung dbu ma'i dbyings su zhugs gnas thim
NK102(ne)004:66: gsum byed pa'i thabs bla ma med pa'i sgyur lam
NK102(ne)004:67: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'di gnyis la rim pa gnyis
NK102(ne)004:69: lam rim pa gnyis su nges pa'i shes byed kyang /
NK102(ne)004:70: sdug bsngal gyi bden pa ji snyed pa thams cad skye shi gnyis su 'du zhing /
NK102(ne)004:71: de'ang skye ba'i rtsa ba can yin pas /
NK102(ne)004:72: skye ba'i rim pa sbyong byed du bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:73: 'chi ba'i rim pa sbyong byed du rdzogs pa'i rim
NK102(ne)004:74: pa ste lam rim pa gnyis su nges pa'i khongs
NK102(ne)004:75: su gsang sngags kyi gzhung ma lus pa 'du zhing
NK102(ne)004:76: / skye ba'i rim pa'ang skye gnas rnam pa bzhir 'dus pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:77: de dang bstun pa'i bskyed rim bsdus 'bring rgyas pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:78: rgyas pa chen po'i bskyed rim dang bzhi yod pa'i
NK102(ne)004:79: skor gsal zhing rgyas pa ni rig 'dzin 'jigs med
NK102(ne)004:80: gling pa'am / mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer gyis mdzad pa
NK102(ne)004:81: bskyed rim lha'i khrid kyi rnam par gzhag pa 'og
NK102(ne)004:82: min bgrod pa'i them skas zhes bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:83: dpal sprul o rgyan 'jigs med chos kyi dbang po
NK102(ne)004:84: mchog gis mdzad pa bskyed rim lha'i khrid kyi dka'
NK102(ne)004:85: gnad cung zad bshad pa las gsal bar bshad yod
NK102(ne)004:87: zhes legs sbyar du b+ha ga wan gyi sgra las drangs pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:88: de'i tshig 'grel du bdud bzhi'i bcom pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:89: rang don du chos kyi sku dang /
NK102(ne)004:90: gzhan don du longs sprul gzugs kyi sku gnyis mngon du byas pas ldan pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:91: srid pa dang zhi ba gnyis ka'i mtha' la mi gnas shing /
NK102(ne)004:92: mya ngan las yongs su 'das pas 'das pa zhes bya /
NK102(ne)004:94: zhes ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin de la /
NK102(ne)004:96: nyes pa'i cha 'bral dgos pa ci zhig kyang med pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:97: 'phags pa thogs med zhabs kyi shes rab kyi pha
NK102(ne)004:98: rol tu phyin pa'i man ngag gi bstan bcos mngon
NK102(ne)004:100: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK102(ne)004:101: gzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK102(ne)004:102: yang dag nyid la yang dag lta //
NK102(ne)004:103: yang dag mthong nas rnam par grol //
NK102(ne)004:104: zhes pa'i 'grel pa slob dpon seng+ge bzang pos mdzad pa las gsal bar bstan pas mtshon /
NK102(ne)004:105: ye gdod ma nas phun sum tshogs pa'i legs tshogs
NK102(ne)004:106: ji snyed pa thams cad ma bsgrubs rang byung lhun
NK102(ne)004:108: dper na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du 'od zer rang chas su bzhugs shing /
NK102(ne)004:109: nyi dkyil dang 'od zer 'du 'bral med pa bzhin no //
NK102(ne)004:111: zhes gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos thams cad ni kun tu bzang po lngar 'dus pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:112: 1ston pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK102(ne)004:113: sangs rgyas thams cad 'og min tu longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:114: chos kyi skur bzhugs bzhin tu sprul pa gdul bya'i
NK102(ne)004:115: gnas ris kun tu 'phro bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK102(ne)004:116: pa / 2gzhi kun tu bzang po ni /
NK102(ne)004:117: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid de /
NK102(ne)004:118: de la ni rang bzhin kun tu bzang po zhes kyang bya /
NK102(ne)004:120: chos thams cad kyi snang ba chos can gyi rol par rang shar ba ste /
NK102(ne)004:121: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag pa /
NK102(ne)004:122: 4rig pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK102(ne)004:123: rang byung gi ye shes bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po /
NK102(ne)004:124: 5rtogs pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK102(ne)004:125: gshis kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin du rtogs pas thar pa dam pa'i mig rnyed pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:126: de la ni lam kun tu bzang po zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:127: de bas na kun tu bzang po zhes su grags shing /
NK102(ne)004:128: sgra don gyi dbang du byas na /
NK102(ne)004:129: dus kun tu nam yang 'khrul pas gos ma myong bas bzang po'i sgras bsnyad pa yin no //
NK102(ne)004:131: zhes gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes kyis mdzad pa'i
NK102(ne)004:132: bstan bcos chen po bsam gtan mig sgron las 'di
NK102(ne)004:134: de la chos thams cad ji bzhin par lta ba ni /
NK102(ne)004:135: khyad par du'ang ma nor ba ste /
NK102(ne)004:137: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid kho na
NK102(ne)004:138: ma bcos ma bslad pa nyid pas a ti yo
NK102(ne)004:140: de'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs ni yon tan gyi cha las snang ba grangs las 'das so //
NK102(ne)004:141: de kho na nyid la dmigs 'dzin med pas gza' gtad dang bral ba zhes bya ba yang grags /
NK102(ne)004:142: de la 'bras bu ril rdzogs pas lhun gyis grub pa zhes bya bar yang grags /
NK102(ne)004:143: de kho nar sdug bsngal ming med pas bde ba chen po zhes bya bar yang grags /
NK102(ne)004:144: gzhan pa'i chos med pas bdag nyid chen por yang grags /
NK102(ne)004:145: zla dang spros pa med pas /
NK102(ne)004:147: de nyid du thams cad du gsal bar gsal bas rang 'byung ye shes su yang grags /
NK102(ne)004:148: 'bras bu la re ba med pas mi rtsol ba'i
NK102(ne)004:149: phyir bya rtsol bral ba zhes bya bar yang grags
NK102(ne)004:150: te / de dag rtags tha dad kyang ngo bo la tha dad med pas /
NK102(ne)004:151: gcig kyang thams cad yin la /
NK102(ne)004:153: gzhi ji bzhin ba'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs so //
NK102(ne)004:154: de lta bas na dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid rtogs par bya'o //
NK102(ne)004:155: de tshul ji bzhin zhe na /
NK102(ne)004:156: ye gza' gtad dang bral ba la gza' gtad dang bral ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:157: ye bdag nyid chen po der lta ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:158: ye lhun gyis grub pa la lhun gyis grub par lta ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:159: ye gnyis su med pa la gnyis su med par lta ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:160: ye bya rtsol dang bral ba la bya rtsol dang bral bar lta ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:161: ye bde ba chen por bde ba chen por lta ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:162: ye thig le chen por lta ba la thig le chen por lta ba'ang med /
NK102(ne)004:163: ye rang 'byung ye shes la rang 'byung ye shes su lta ba'ang med pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)004:164: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid ji bzhin pa'i chos la de nyid du'ang mi lta'o //
NK102(ne)004:165: zhes pas gsal ba'i ji bzhin ba'i klong chen po
NK102(ne)004:166: de nyid mngon du gyur cing de nyid kyi klong
NK102(ne)004:168: skabs 'dir ji bzhin ba zhes dang /
NK102(ne)004:169: ji bzhin pa zhes 'bri stangs mi 'dra ba gnyis
NK102(ne)004:170: su yod 'dug pa de ni gna' bo'i dpe rnying
NK102(ne)004:171: rnams su ji bzhin ba zhes pa kho nar snang
NK102(ne)004:172: la / deng dus kyi lugs su ni ji bzhin pa zhes 'byung bas 'gal ba gang yang med /
NK102(ne)004:173: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:174: zhes kun gzhi dbyings su nub cing gti mug gnas
NK102(ne)004:175: dag pa ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes te
NK102(ne)004:176: / de kho na nyid bsgoms pas chos dbyings ye shes la sgrib pa bsal nas snang zhing /
NK102(ne)004:177: chos nyid spros pa zhi ba'i ngo bo mkhyen pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:179: zhes chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ye shes
NK102(ne)004:180: kyi klong chen por ji tsam du bzhugs pa de
NK102(ne)004:181: snyed du kun tu rtog pa'i 'ching ba las yongs
NK102(ne)004:185: had de bar lus pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:186: g.yeng bas 'byams te dran rig dang bral zhing /
NK102(ne)004:187: rtog pa med pa de dag gi gnas skabs rnams la rtog med kyi tha snyad 'jug mod /
NK102(ne)004:188: skabs 'dir bstan gyi rtog med ni /
NK102(ne)004:189: su zhig bsam gtan la blo rtse gcig pas gnas
NK102(ne)004:190: pa'i skabs der bzang ngan gyi rtog pa ci zhig
NK102(ne)004:191: kyang mi 'char bar rtog med du gnas shing /
NK102(ne)004:192: de'ang ji ltar rdul sogs rnyogs ma'i chus khengs pa'i
NK102(ne)004:193: bum pa de 'gul skyod kyis ma bslad par rang
NK102(ne)004:194: babs su lhan ner bzhag pas /
NK102(ne)004:195: rnyogs pa dang dwangs ma'i chu rim gyis kha zhabs phyed cing /
NK102(ne)004:196: rang babs kyi ngang tshul rjen par 'char ba dang
NK102(ne)004:197: tshul mthun pa'i bsam gtan kun rtog gi gzhan dbang
NK102(ne)004:198: du ma gyur pa de la zer ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:199: sgom chen pas sems rtog med du zin pa'i cha de dang /
NK102(ne)004:200: rnal 'byor pas rig pa rtog med du rjen par
NK102(ne)004:201: ngos zin pa gnyis rtog med tsam du 'dra na'ang
NK102(ne)004:202: / sems rtog med ni lus gnad la sogs pa gzhig na zhig par 'gyur zhing /
NK102(ne)004:203: rjen la'ang ma bud pa zhig yin la /
NK102(ne)004:204: rig pa rtog med ni gnas tshul de las bzlog
NK102(ne)004:205: pa'i khyad shin tu che bar yod pa'i tshul kun
NK102(ne)004:206: mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams pa dri med 'od zer
NK102(ne)004:207: gyis chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las gsal bar
NK102(ne)004:208: gsungs yod pa de bzhin du shes so //
NK102(ne)004:211: snang ba yab la stong pa yum ste /
NK102(ne)004:212: yab yum gnyis kyis snang stong gnyis mtshon pa'i dbang gis /
NK102(ne)004:213: thabs kyi cha thams cad bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po dang /
NK102(ne)004:214: bde gshegs rigs lnga sogs snang ba yab kyis mtshon pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:215: shes rab kyi cha thams cad bcom ldan 'das ma dpal kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK102(ne)004:216: bde gshegs yum chen lnga sogs stong pa yum gyi mtshon pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:218: zhes sbas pa'i rgum chung gi rtsa ba'i gzhung 'di'i
NK102(ne)004:219: dgongs pa don rnam pa lngar bkral ba de nyid
NK102(ne)004:220: kyis che ba rnam pa lnga ste /
NK102(ne)004:221: 1kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin la phyag 'tshal bar bstan pas che ba /
NK102(ne)004:222: 2byang chub kyi sems kyi rang bzhin bstan pas che ba /
NK102(ne)004:223: 3byang chub kyi sems kyi dpe mi dmigs par bstan pas che ba /
NK102(ne)004:224: 4kun gzhi mkha' dbyings rnam par dag par bstan pas che ba /
NK102(ne)004:225: 5byang chub sems kyi gol sa dang sgrib pa bstan pas che ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:226: mye long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:227: zhes kun gzhi'i rnam shes nub cing zhe sdang gnas
NK102(ne)004:228: su dag pa ni me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK102(ne)004:229: te / dper na me long gi ngogs su gang bstan pa'i rkyen de gsal por 'char ba ltar /
NK102(ne)004:230: rig pa dri med la ye shes dag pa'i snang ba yongs su gsal zhing /
NK102(ne)004:231: chos kyi tshig don 'dzin pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:232: chos rnams kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal bar ngang gis mkhyen pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:234: zhes zag bcas dang zag med kyi chos gang zhig
NK102(ne)004:235: blo'i yul du byas pa lta bu zhig min na'ang
NK102(ne)004:236: / rtog med de rang blo'i yul du byed pa
NK102(ne)004:237: ni ming med ces pa de rang ming du song
NK102(ne)004:239: blo yi yul du snang zhes gsungs pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:240: dpe 'dir blo yi yul du snang yin /
NK102(ne)004:241: zhes tshig rkang gcig byed pa la tshig gcig ma
NK102(ne)004:242: tshang ba de ni byed tshig snang ba zhes pa'i
NK102(ne)004:243: tshig mtha' chad pa zhig yin pa ni shes par
NK102(ne)004:244: sla'o // gnyis su myed pa'i byang chub kyi sems /
NK102(ne)004:245: zhes gnyis su med pa'i don ni /
NK102(ne)004:246: yod pa dang med pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:247: rtag pa dang chad pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:248: gcig dang du ma gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:249: skyes pa dang ma skyes pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:250: nyin mo dang mtshan mo gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:251: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:254: rtsol ba dang mi rtsol ba gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:255: thob pa dang ma thob pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:256: rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:257: bsgom pa dang mi bsgom pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:258: byung tshor ldang ba dang mi ldang ba gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:259: mnyam par bzhag pa dang ma bzhag pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:260: grags pa dang ma grags pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:261: bzang ba dang ngan pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:263: 'gags pa dang mi 'gags pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:264: gnas pa dang mi gnas pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:271: spyod pa dang mi spyod pa gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:288: mtho ris ngan song gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:291: 'bras bu tshol ma tshol gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:292: sangs rgyas kyi sa non ma non gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:294: snying rje mi rje gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:298: btang snyoms byas ma byas gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:303: lta ba dang lta byed gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:304: gtan tshigs kyis gzhal ba dang mi 'jal ba gnyis med /
NK102(ne)004:305: bden pa gnyis med sogs te bsam gtan mig sgron
NK102(ne)004:306: las zhib rgyas bstan pa'i gnyis med kyi bdag nyid
NK102(ne)004:307: ye gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems dam pa
NK102(ne)004:309: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:310: zhes nyon mongs pa'i yid nub cing nga rgyal gnas su dag pa mnyam nyid ye shes te /
NK102(ne)004:311: chos kun mnyam pa'i ngo bor phyogs gang du'ang ma lhung zhing /
NK102(ne)004:313: mnyam pa'i rkyen snang ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:315: gnyis su med par rtog pa gsum rnams /
NK102(ne)004:316: mnyam dus mthar phyin 'bras bu'i dus su mngon du gyur pas /
NK102(ne)004:317: mnyam pa'i tshad zad sar skyol zhing /
NK102(ne)004:318: thams cad mnyam pa nyid ro gcig par mkhyen pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:320: zhes mdo lugs su zhi gnas rtse gcig pa'i ngang
NK102(ne)004:321: rnam rtog yul thog tu mi 'phro bar gnas pa
NK102(ne)004:322: de la mi rtog pa zhes su grags la /
NK102(ne)004:323: sngags lugs su kun rtog gnyis 'dzin gyi gzhan dbang
NK102(ne)004:324: du mi 'gyur ba snang stong dbyer med chen po'i
NK102(ne)004:325: ngang mi rtog par gnas pa de la mi rtog
NK102(ne)004:326: pa zhes su grags pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:327: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i skabs 'dir sems gnas pa'ang /
NK102(ne)004:328: 'gyu zhing 'phro ba gang zhig yin yang rung /
NK102(ne)004:329: don du rig pa byang chub sems kyi rang rtsal lam /
NK102(ne)004:331: rgyan tsam las gzhan du med pas /
NK102(ne)004:332: gnas pa'am 'gyu ba gang gi skabs yin kyang rung /
NK102(ne)004:333: da lta'i shes pa skad cig ma gsal tsam rig
NK102(ne)004:334: tsam pa'i ngang nyid chen po de ga'i gshis thog
NK102(ne)004:335: tu gnas pa la mi rtog zab mo zhes bya
NK102(ne)004:336: ba yin / de'i tshul bsam gtan mig sgron las kyang 'di skad ces gsungs te /
NK102(ne)004:337: mi rtog pa ni 'jig rten pa'i mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:338: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:340: de la 'jig rten pa'i mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:341: bsam gtan bzhi dang snyoms par 'jug bzhi pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:342: 'jig rten las 'das pa ni nyan thos 'gog pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:343: rang rgyal zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK102(ne)004:344: de ni byis pa nyer spyod kyi bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)004:345: bla ma'i mi rtog pa ni theg pa chen po ste /
NK102(ne)004:346: de la don rab 'byed pa'i bsam gtan lhag mthong ste /
NK102(ne)004:347: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi rgyu las byung ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:348: de bzhin nyid dmigs kyi bsam gtan ni mtshan ma med pa'i zhi gnas so //
NK102(ne)004:349: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bsam gtan ni zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:350: de dag la'ang mos pa las byung ba'i mi dmigs pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:351: shin tu mi dmigs pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:352: rjes su mi dmigs par bshad de go sla bas ma sbyar ro //
NK102(ne)004:354: snang la mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:355: mi snang la mi rtog pa gnyis las /
NK102(ne)004:356: snang la mi rtog pa ni gnyis te /
NK102(ne)004:357: mtshan mar snang la mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:358: dang po ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:359: mig sogs kyi dbang po yul la rten 'brel gzhan
NK102(ne)004:360: dbang la dmigs pa'i shes pa rtog med kyi 'dzin
NK102(ne)004:361: pa dang bral ba rnams so //
NK102(ne)004:362: ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa yang gsum ste /
NK102(ne)004:363: yod pa'i ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:364: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i gzhan gyi dbang rten 'brel las
NK102(ne)004:365: byung ba sgyu ma tsam pas rang rgyud pa'i rtog
NK102(ne)004:366: pa med yid la byed pa'i shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:367: mu stegs can dag gi bdag tu yid la byed
NK102(ne)004:368: pa'i shes pa gzhan med par yid kyang de la
NK102(ne)004:370: stong pa'i ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:371: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i yongs su grub pa bsgom pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:372: dbu ma'i lam sgom pa'i shes pa lhag mthong ste /
NK102(ne)004:373: de la gong gi mi dmigs pa tshang ngo //
NK102(ne)004:374: de las khyad du gnyis su med pa'i mi rtog pa ma h+aa yo ga'o //
NK102(ne)004:375: lhun gyis grub pa'i mi rtog pa chen po a ti yo ga'o zhes so //
NK102(ne)004:379: sdug bsngal gyis bsdus pa'i chos kun brtags na med la /
NK102(ne)004:381: byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po'i klong dag pa /
NK102(ne)004:382: zug rngu ma spangs bde ba chen po rang shar
NK102(ne)004:383: ba la bde ba chen po zhes bya ba de'i
NK102(ne)004:384: tha snyad kyi brjod pa ma 'gags kyang brjod du
NK102(ne)004:385: cang med pa / blos kyang bde ba chen po
NK102(ne)004:386: zhes gzung du ye bral ba ni 'di ltar snang
NK102(ne)004:388: gzhan nas btsal du med cing /
NK102(ne)004:389: de lta bu'i don gyi gnad chud pas rang rig pa bde ba chen por gsal ba ni /
NK102(ne)004:390: ngan song 'khor ba nyid bde ba chen por gsal
NK102(ne)004:391: bas spyod yul ma bkol dag pa'i tshul bsam gtan
NK102(ne)004:394: zhes so sor rtog pa'i ye shes zhes pa'i don te /
NK102(ne)004:395: de ni yid shes nub cing 'dod chags gnas su dag pas /
NK102(ne)004:396: bya byed bral ba'i rig par rtogs pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:397: dbang po'i rigs gang la gang snang ba de'i chos
NK102(ne)004:398: rim pa so sor gsal zhing shes bya thogs med
NK102(ne)004:399: du mkhyen pa'o // myi rtog pa chen po /
NK102(ne)004:400: zhes gong du myi rtog zab mo zhes bya ba de dang don gcig pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:402: zhes bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes sam /
NK102(ne)004:403: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes zhes pa'i don te /
NK102(ne)004:404: de ni sgo lnga'i rnam shes nub cing phrag dog gnas su dag pas /
NK102(ne)004:405: cir yang rig pa'i ngang nyid du rdzogs te /
NK102(ne)004:407: chos kun rang gzhag rang grol shes bya thogs med du mkhyen pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:409: zhes gong du ji bzhin ba'i klong zhes bya ba'i
NK102(ne)004:410: yin lugs chen po de'i ngang nyid du shar ba'i
NK102(ne)004:411: rtsal gyi chos ji ltar shel sgang las sna tshogs
NK102(ne)004:412: pa'i 'ja' 'od 'gags med du 'phro zhing kun tu
NK102(ne)004:413: snang na'ang / rtsal gyi chos dag ma dag gang
NK102(ne)004:414: zhig snang ba de ni yongs su dag pa'i shel
NK102(ne)004:415: sgang de'i rgyan nam yon tan du shar ba las
NK102(ne)004:416: snang na'ang / / des rang bzhin la phan gnod
NK102(ne)004:417: gang yang med pa des mtshon pa'i chos rnams la
NK102(ne)004:418: snang na'ang / / bya ba yin / rig pa'i rgyal po /
NK102(ne)004:419: zhes gzhi'i gnas lugs ngo bo stong pa /
NK102(ne)004:421: thugs rje 'gags med bcas gzhir gnas kyi ye shes
NK102(ne)004:422: sum ldan du bzhugs pa'i gnas lugs zab mo de
NK102(ne)004:423: nyid ji bzhin par rig cing rtogs pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:428: man ngag sogs kun gyi mchog gam /
NK102(ne)004:430: rgyal po yin pas rig pa'i rgyal po zhes su grags pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:434: smon pa med pa ste rnam thar sgo gsum gyi
NK102(ne)004:435: bdag nyid de la stong pa chen po zhes bya
NK102(ne)004:436: la / de'i tshul ji ltar yin lugs gsal bar bsnyad pa'i don no //
NK102(ne)004:438: zhes sangs rgyas dang byang sems sogs skyes mchog dam
NK102(ne)004:439: pa rnams kyis gsungs pa'i tshig bslu ba med pa
NK102(ne)004:441: shin tu lkog gyur gyi chos rnams la nges shes
NK102(ne)004:442: rnyed pa'i bden dpangs su drangs pa de rigs la
NK102(ne)004:443: lung zhes bya ba'i skabs dang /
NK102(ne)004:444: ston pa sangs rgyas kyi bka' mdo rgyud ci rigs dang /
NK102(ne)004:445: gzhan yang rjes 'jug mkhas pas mdzad pa'i bstan bcos /
NK102(ne)004:446: drang srong rigs sngags grub pa rnams kyis bstan pa'i sngags dang /
NK102(ne)004:447: las sna tshogs pa'i gzhung ci'ang rung ba de dag la 'jug tu rung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:448: zhugs pas nges par grub pa'i bzlas lung ste /
NK102(ne)004:449: gzhung gang yang rung ba de'i sgra tshig dag par
NK102(ne)004:450: rna ba'i dbang por thos nges su brjod cing ngag
NK102(ne)004:451: nus rim par brgyud pas nus ldan du bsgrub pa
NK102(ne)004:452: de la lung zhes bya ba'i skabs dang /
NK102(ne)004:453: nang rgyud sde gsum du ston pa sku gsum gyis bstan pa'i rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK102(ne)004:455: yan lag gi rgyud ci'ang rung ba de dag las
NK102(ne)004:456: snying po'i gnad thor bur blangs pa de rigs la
NK102(ne)004:457: lung zhes bya ba'i skabs te rnam pa gsum yod
NK102(ne)004:458: pa las / skabs 'dir bstan gyi lung ni phyi ma 'di nyid yin la /
NK102(ne)004:459: karma pa rang byung rdo rje mchog gis mdzad pa'i gzhung rgya mtsho mtha' yas las kyang /
NK102(ne)004:460: rgyud sde chen po rnams kyi nang nas /
NK102(ne)004:461: lung khyad par du 'phags pa sna tshogs btus nas /
NK102(ne)004:462: lung gi sgra don mang po gtan la 'bebs pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:463: lung zhes pa'i don de ga yin cing /
NK102(ne)004:465: mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa la'ang lung bcu gnyis pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:466: de las 'phros pa sum cu rtsa drug gis gtan
NK102(ne)004:467: la 'bebs pa btus pa'i rgyud du grags shing dpal
NK102(ne)004:469: thog ma'i sangs rgyas kyi lung las btus nas gsungs pas /
NK102(ne)004:470: btus pa'i rgyud a nu yo gar gtogs par 'dod pa'ang yod /
NK102(ne)004:471: ces gsal bar bstan pas shes thub /
NK102(ne)004:473: thun mong ma yin pa'i ngag ces bya ba'i don te /
NK102(ne)004:474: de ni skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis gdams pa
NK102(ne)004:475: nyams su len pa'i tshe khyad par can gyi myong
NK102(ne)004:476: ba ci dang ci byung ba de dag phyi rabs
NK102(ne)004:477: gdul bya rnams kyi don du thun mong ma yin
NK102(ne)004:478: par gsang ba'i sgo nas snyan du brgyud pa'i ngag
NK102(ne)004:479: gam / snyan du brgyud pa'i ngag 'ga' zhig yi
NK102(ne)004:480: ger bkod pa de dag la man ngag tu grags
NK102(ne)004:484: mngon pa'i sde snod de thun mong theg par grags che ba'i sde snod gsum mam /
NK102(ne)004:487: rig 'dzin sngags kyi sde snod de bla med theg
NK102(ne)004:488: par grags che ba'i sde snod gsum bcas gtso che'i
NK102(ne)004:489: sgo nas ngos 'dzin tshul mi 'dra ba gnyis yod
NK102(ne)004:490: cing / de gnyis kyang 'gal ba med de /
NK102(ne)004:491: mngon pa'i don mthar thug pa ni rig pa 'dzin
NK102(ne)004:492: pa'i gzhung rnams nas legs par bstan pa'i de kho
NK102(ne)004:493: na nyid de ka yin la /
NK102(ne)004:494: rig 'dzin sngags kyi sde snod kyi bstan bya gtso
NK102(ne)004:495: bo'ang mngon pa nyid las ma 'das pas de gnyis
NK102(ne)004:496: gcig tu byas pa yin no //
NK102(ne)004:498: zhes thun mong theg pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK102(ne)004:499: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK102(ne)004:500: don dam byang chub kyi sems gnyis yod /
NK102(ne)004:501: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems la /
NK102(ne)004:502: lam du 'gro bar 'dod pa lta bu smon pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK102(ne)004:503: lam du dngos su zhugs pa lta bu phar phyir
NK102(ne)004:504: drug la dngos su slob pa 'jug pa byang chub
NK102(ne)004:506: don dam byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK102(ne)004:507: tshogs sbyor gyi lam du sems bskyed pa la brten nas blo sbyangs pas /
NK102(ne)004:508: mthar mthong lam du chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs
NK102(ne)004:509: spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes stong pa nyid
NK102(ne)004:510: kyi don mngon sum du rtogs pa de yin /
NK102(ne)004:512: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes spros pa'i mtha'
NK102(ne)004:513: thams cad dang yongs su bral ba de la ye
NK102(ne)004:514: gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems zhes pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:515: tshig bsdus pa'i dbang gis byang chub kyi sems zhes dang /
NK102(ne)004:516: byang sems dang byang chub dang /
NK102(ne)004:517: skabs 'gar sems zhes pa'i tshig gcig pu 'byung ba'i skabs kyang yod /
NK102(ne)004:518: 'on kyang de skabs kyi brjod bya'i don dang /
NK102(ne)004:519: de dang 'brel ba khyad chos kyi tshig tshogs ci rigs pas nges shes thub par brten /
NK102(ne)004:521: kun tu rtog pa'i sems nor ba'i skabs mi yong /
NK102(ne)004:522: byang chub kyi sems de la mtshan gyi rnam grangs gzhan ni /
NK102(ne)004:528: rang byung ye shes chos kyi dbyings sogs mang du snang mod /
NK102(ne)004:529: don du ye gdod ma nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:530: shes bya'i sgrib pa ci zhig gis kyang gos ma myong bas /
NK102(ne)004:531: spang bya'i dri ma dang yongs su bral la ka nas dag pas byang ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:532: legs pa'i yon tan thams cad kyang ma bsgrubs ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs shing /
NK102(ne)004:533: rtogs bya'i chos kun bslab rtsol la ltos ma dgos
NK102(ne)004:534: par ji ltar nyi ma'i rang bzhin 'od zer dang
NK102(ne)004:535: / me long gi rang bzhin gsal la dag pa
NK102(ne)004:536: dang 'dra ba chos kun yongs su chub pa dang
NK102(ne)004:537: / / de'ang kun rdzob 'khor 'das kyi chos su
NK102(ne)004:538: shar ba'i sems dang sems byung kun gyi 'char gzhi
NK102(ne)004:539: / / sems nyid dam / sems kyi de bzhin nyid yin pas sems te /
NK102(ne)004:540: byang chub kyi sems zhes rdzogs chen a ti yo
NK102(ne)004:541: ga sems klong man ngag gi sde tshang ma'i rgyud
NK102(ne)004:542: lung man ngag gi gzhung rnams su yongs su grags
NK102(ne)004:545: yul kun tu rtog pa'i sems de ni rig byed rtsal lam /
NK102(ne)004:547: de la byang chub kyi sems zer ba min /
NK102(ne)004:548: byang chub kyi sems ni dngos po dang /
NK102(ne)004:549: mtshan ma'i chos kun las 'das pa /
NK102(ne)004:550: stong gsal spros pa dang bral ba /
NK102(ne)004:551: 'di dang 'adi'o zhes dmigs su med pa /
NK102(ne)004:555: ngos gzung 'os pa ci zhig kyang med pas dper bzhag pa'i chos kyang med la /
NK102(ne)004:556: dpe des mtshon pa'i don byang chub kyi sems rang
NK102(ne)004:557: bzhin gyis dag pa nyid gang du'ang grub pa med
NK102(ne)004:558: mod / nam mkha'i ngang du snod bcud kun 'dus pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:559: byang chub kyi sems de'i ngang du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yin zhing /
NK102(ne)004:560: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin me long lta bu'i
NK102(ne)004:561: ngang na rang rtsal gzugs brnyan dang 'dra ba snang
NK102(ne)004:562: srid kyi chos kun 'gags med du 'char ba'i gzhir
NK102(ne)004:563: gnas pas / snod bcud kyi snang ba sna tshogs su shar yang /
NK102(ne)004:564: byang chub kyi sems kyi ngo bo la gos pa
NK102(ne)004:565: dang 'pho 'gyur ci'ang mi mnga' ba ni ji ltar
NK102(ne)004:566: gzugs brnyan gyis me long la ma gos shing /
NK102(ne)004:567: me long gi rang bzhin la 'pho 'gyur ci'ang mi byed pa dang 'dra ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:569: zhes byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po'i ngang
NK102(ne)004:570: la so sor rang gis rig pa'i lta ba mi
NK102(ne)004:572: rig pa'i ye shes la chos kun gsal bas chad par lta bu'i gol sa las grol ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:573: yod med dang mtshan ma'i rjes su mi 'brang bas g.yeng ba'i gol sa las grol ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:574: tshogs drug rang grol du bzhag pas rnam par rtog
NK102(ne)004:575: pa'i byung tshor 'gegs shing zhi bar byed pa'i nyan
NK102(ne)004:576: thos kyi gol lam las grol ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:577: gnyis su med pa'i ngang der gang gis gang la chags pa myed pas /
NK102(ne)004:578: zhi ba'i ro la chags nas mya ngan las 'das
NK102(ne)004:579: pa'i mtha' zhi ba phyogs gcig pa rang rgyal gyi
NK102(ne)004:580: gol lam las grol ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:581: ye shes chen po'i ngang la mi rtog stong par byar med pas /
NK102(ne)004:582: bden pa gnyis su lta ba'i byang sems theg pa'i gol lam las grol ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:583: de yang bsam gtan mig sgron las ye nas mu
NK102(ne)004:584: mtha' med pa'i don la kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam
NK102(ne)004:585: du lta la / don dam par ma skyes pa lta na mdo sder gol ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:587: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis stong pa lus ngag
NK102(ne)004:588: yid gsum skyon ci yang stong pa nyid yin pas
NK102(ne)004:589: lus stong zhing dben pa ngag dang yid kyang stong
NK102(ne)004:590: zhing dben pas / dgon pa gsum la gnas pa
NK102(ne)004:591: des grub par lta na ston mun du gol ba'o
NK102(ne)004:593: 'dir ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid kyi klong la ngo bor bzung du med bzhin du /
NK102(ne)004:594: byang chub sems dpa' rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i gol sa
NK102(ne)004:595: 'od dang thig le'i rang bzhin rtag pa can du
NK102(ne)004:596: bzung nas bsgom pas lus 'dar ba bde ba skye
NK102(ne)004:597: bar 'dod na la sogs pa byung na sngags su
NK102(ne)004:599: rnam gcig tu bskyed pa'i rim pas gol ba phung
NK102(ne)004:600: po khams skye mched lhar bsgoms te rtog pa kun
NK102(ne)004:601: btags log ces dang po byung nas /
NK102(ne)004:602: yang dag zhen pa 'jug de la yang mi gnas
NK102(ne)004:603: par byed pa ni sngags kyi mtshan mar gol ba'o
NK102(ne)004:605: sngags kyi de bzhin nyid du gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)004:606: ma h+aa yo ga pa ni chos thams cad rang
NK102(ne)004:607: rig pa'i ye shes dus gsum mnyam pa chen po
NK102(ne)004:608: / de bzhin nyid la blo 'jug pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:609: bsgom pa dang dang ldan pa yod na bdag nyid chen po bya ba med par ma shes so //
NK102(ne)004:611: a nu yo gar gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)004:612: ma h+aa yo ga ni ci yang ched du byed /
NK102(ne)004:613: de las khyad par 'phags par gsal ba'i a nu yo ga yang /
NK102(ne)004:615: ched du bya ba med pa skad zer yang /
NK102(ne)004:618: kha dog grangs kyi rtsol ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:621: mi dmigs pa'i ngang skad cig mas lha grangs med
NK102(ne)004:622: du bskyed cing don byed pa nyid la mthong ste
NK102(ne)004:626: lus kyi sgo nas phyag 'tshal dang /
NK102(ne)004:627: ngag gi sgo nas kha ton bzlas brjod byed pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:628: yid kyi sgo nas dad cing dang ba 'dren pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:629: mthol bshags byed pa sogs mdor na sgo gsum gyi
NK102(ne)004:630: byed rtsol mi 'dra ba du ma la brten nas
NK102(ne)004:631: bsod nams dge ba'i tshogs rgya chen po bsags te
NK102(ne)004:632: ye shes kyi tshogs dam pa la 'jug pa'i cha
NK102(ne)004:633: rkyen yang dag par bsgrub pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:636: mdo sngags kyi lugs gang zhig yin kyang rung /
NK102(ne)004:637: lam gyi cha rkyen bsod nams kyi tshogs la brten nas /
NK102(ne)004:638: rim gyis sems gnas kyi rim pa ci rigs par 'jug cing /
NK102(ne)004:640: lhag mthong ye shes kyi tshogs rgya chen po bsgrubs
NK102(ne)004:641: te bla na med pa'i byang chub dam pa mngon
NK102(ne)004:644: zhes brda rnying ma'i lugs shig ste /
NK102(ne)004:645: deng dus kyi dbang du byas na /
NK102(ne)004:647: la sogs pa zhes pa dang don gcig yin /
NK102(ne)004:649: zhes slob dpon kun bzang rdo rje mchog gis mdzad
NK102(ne)004:650: pa snyan brgyud rin po che rdo rje zam pa'i
NK102(ne)004:651: gdam ngag gzhung bshad che ba zhes pa las 'di
NK102(ne)004:653: ting nge 'dzin la yang sgros rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK102(ne)004:654: 1'dzin pa rtse gcig gi ting nge 'dzin /
NK102(ne)004:655: 2khyab pa mtha' dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK102(ne)004:656: 3gnyug ma lhun grub kyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK102(ne)004:657: 4rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang bzhi'o //
NK102(ne)004:658: 1'dzin pa rtse gcig gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK102(ne)004:659: mu stegs rtag pa po yod par lta ba'am /
NK102(ne)004:660: chad pa po med par 'dzin pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:661: gsang sngags zung 'jug bden par 'dzin pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:662: phyag rgya chen po pa snang stong dbyer med du 'dod pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:663: pha rol tu phyin pa dbyer med brjod du med par 'dod pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:664: de rnams ni theg pa gong ma'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK102(ne)004:665: ting nge 'dzin de la phyogs su 'dzin pa'i mtha'
NK102(ne)004:666: zab cing phra ba tsam yang yod pa ma yin
NK102(ne)004:667: pas 'dzin pa rtse gcig gi ting nge 'dzin no
NK102(ne)004:668: // 2ting 'dzin de thams cad kyang rang gi sems
NK102(ne)004:669: su ma spangs pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i sems nyid
NK102(ne)004:670: de'ang gsal ba mi rtog pa bde ba ngo bo
NK102(ne)004:671: dbyer mi phyed pa gcig tu rtogs pas /
NK102(ne)004:672: 'dzin pa rtse gcig gi ting nge 'dzin yang ma
NK102(ne)004:673: spangs la ye nas lhun gyis grub pa dbyer mi
NK102(ne)004:674: phyed pa'i dus na dbyer mi phyed bya ba'i khyab
NK102(ne)004:675: pa / dbyer mi phyed bya bar mi phyed bya
NK102(ne)004:676: ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra
NK102(ne)004:677: ba tsam yang mi gnas pas khyab pa dang bral
NK102(ne)004:679: 3mtha' dang bral ba'i don ma byas na ma bcos
NK102(ne)004:680: pa'i gnyug ma de la don thams cad lhun gyis
NK102(ne)004:681: grub pas na gnyug ma lhun grub kyi ting nge
NK102(ne)004:682: 'dzin no // 4don de la blo'i rnam par gang yang mi gnas te /
NK102(ne)004:683: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas na rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK102(ne)004:684: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa de la ni
NK102(ne)004:685: bsam pa'i blo'am brjod pa'i tshig dang bral ba'i don
NK102(ne)004:686: zab mo de la mi 'gyur bas na ting nge
NK102(ne)004:689: zhes spyir na bag chags zhes pa ni las dang
NK102(ne)004:690: nyon mongs pa'i rjes shul lus pa dper na dri
NK102(ne)004:691: bzang gi snod du dri bzang med na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:692: de'i shul lam bag yun ring du chags pa lta bu zhig la zer ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:693: skabs 'dir ting nge 'dzin gyi bag chags sbyang dgos pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:694: phyi rgyud sde gsum skabs lha'i mngon zhen gyi bag chags dang /
NK102(ne)004:695: nang rgyud sde gsum gyi skabs ting 'dzin bde ba'i
NK102(ne)004:696: ro la zhen pa'i bag chags nas shes sgrib phra
NK102(ne)004:699: zhes bsam mno rtse gcig pa dmigs pa'i rten mtshan
NK102(ne)004:700: bcas sam mtshan med gang yang rung bar gtad pa
NK102(ne)004:701: na kun rtog gis ma g.yos pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:702: g.yo ma nus pa brtan par gnas pa'i zhi gnas te /
NK102(ne)004:703: de ni pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi nang
NK102(ne)004:704: tshan du gyur pa'i bsam gtan dang gcig pa yin
NK102(ne)004:706: zhes bsam gtan du mnyam par gnas pa'i skabs myong
NK102(ne)004:707: zhing tshor ba'i bde ba'i ro smra bsam brjod pa
NK102(ne)004:708: las 'das na'ang / ji ltar lkugs pas bu ram
NK102(ne)004:709: gyi ro myong ba ltar zad mi shes pa'i bde
NK102(ne)004:710: ba khyad par can myong ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:712: zhes phyir snang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i gzugs sgra
NK102(ne)004:713: dri ro reg bya'i chos de dag phyi nang gang
NK102(ne)004:714: du'ang med kyang / yul gyi bag chags kyis phyi
NK102(ne)004:715: rol tu yod pa ltar snang ba sems la shar
NK102(ne)004:716: du'ang med kyang / nas / de dag la don
NK102(ne)004:717: du mngon par zhen te dgag sgrub tu 'dzin pa'i
NK102(ne)004:718: yul byed pa la gzung ba zhes bya zhing /
NK102(ne)004:719: zhen yul de la 'di ni gzugs so //
NK102(ne)004:721: zhes sogs phyi rol tu rtog pa de la gzung ba'i rtog pa zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:722: bag chags sna tshogs pa'i kun gzhi la brten nas kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:723: de las mched pa mig gi rnam par shes pa sogs lnga dang /
NK102(ne)004:724: dbang pos yul rig pa'i rjes su yid kyi shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:725: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid de rnam pa brgyad
NK102(ne)004:726: yod pa de dag la 'dzin pa'i sems sam 'dzin
NK102(ne)004:728: de rnams la rtog pa de la ni 'dzin pa'i rtog pa zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:729: 'dzin pa zhes bya ba'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK102(ne)004:730: kun gzhi bag chags kyi sa pa de ni ngo bo ma rig pa /
NK102(ne)004:731: rnam pa snang yul gang dang yang ma 'brel ba'i
NK102(ne)004:732: rtog med tsam du gnas pas gzugs med pa'i bag
NK102(ne)004:734: de'i ngang las gsal dwangs rig pa'i cha tsam shar
NK102(ne)004:735: zhing yul dang ma 'brel ba de ni kun gzhi'i
NK102(ne)004:737: des ni gzugs kyi bag chags 'dzin cing /
NK102(ne)004:738: de las mched pa sgo lnga'i rnam shes rtog med
NK102(ne)004:739: dag gis kyang gzugs kyis pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK102(ne)004:741: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang /
NK102(ne)004:742: yid kyi shes pa gnyis kyis ni 'dod pa'i bag chags 'dzin pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:743: tshogs brgyad po de dag gis rang rang gi yul rtog pa med pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:744: rtog pa dang bcas pas 'dzin pa yin pa'i phyir na 'dzin pa zhes su grags pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:746: zhes bsam gtan mig sgron las /
NK102(ne)004:747: de la lus kyi bzhag thabs ni /
NK102(ne)004:748: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor man chad lhang lus bcos la bzhag pa med de /
NK102(ne)004:749: lus 'dzin pa'i 'du shes dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)004:750: lus pa 'dug thabs nges par bzhag pa med do //
NK102(ne)004:751: 'o na 'og ma'i skyil mo krung la sogs pa dgag gam zhe na /
NK102(ne)004:752: lus su ma dmigs phan chad dgag tu med de /
NK102(ne)004:753: ched du dang du len pa med na /
NK102(ne)004:754: skyil mo la sogs pa gan rkyal kha sbub gang du 'gre yang 'gal ba med do //
NK102(ne)004:755: rnal 'byor nyid gang bde bar bya ste /
NK102(ne)004:756: snyoms las kyis ni bya ba ma yin no //
NK102(ne)004:757: de'i yid ches par bya ba'i rgyab gnon du /
NK102(ne)004:759: lus sems ma skyes gzhi med pas //
NK102(ne)004:760: kha ltar bcos pa'i kha na med //
NK102(ne)004:763: sgyu ma bzhin du lus shes na //
NK102(ne)004:765: spyod lam gsum gyis gnas pa gang //
NK102(ne)004:766: ched du bya med byed pa'ang med //
NK102(ne)004:769: gang la gnas gzhi rten med pas //
NK102(ne)004:770: gnas der lus bcos kha na med //
NK102(ne)004:772: bsam gtan lus dben bcos mi bya //
NK102(ne)004:773: de la de dben ma bcos pa //
NK102(ne)004:774: de nyid ye nas ye shesdben pa'i gnas //
NK102(ne)004:777: mtha' yas zhing khams bdag lus phyir //
NK102(ne)004:778: rnam pa'i lus ngan ma spangs bral //
NK102(ne)004:779: lus su dben pa'ang dben pa'i phyir //
NK102(ne)004:780: skyil krung drang por 'dug pa'ang med //
NK102(ne)004:782: lus bying bzhag thabs bya ba med pas /
NK102(ne)004:783: byas pa mi 'gog par bzhed do //
NK102(ne)004:784: 'o na bcos pa'i skyon ji lta bu zhe na /
NK102(ne)004:785: gang lus 'chos pa la ni da rung lus su 'dzin pa yod de /
NK102(ne)004:786: 'dzin pas nam du yang don mthong bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)004:788: tshad mar lus sems 'chos byed pa //
NK102(ne)004:789: 'dzin pa'i phur pa de la yod //
NK102(ne)004:792: zhen pas spyod lam bcos spyod byed pa //
NK102(ne)004:793: de ni lus bcos spyod bslad pa yin //
NK102(ne)004:796: yang bsam gtan mig sgron las /
NK102(ne)004:797: de lta bu mi shes par sgo gsum ched du 'chos shing rtsol ba ni /
NK102(ne)004:798: 'dzin pa'i phur pa dang sgrib pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:800: bcos su med pa la bcos pa nyid rtog pa'i 'dzin pa dang phur pa'o //
NK102(ne)004:803: zhes tshig 'di ni rdzogs chen gyi rgyud lung rnams su shin tu grags che ba zhig ste /
NK102(ne)004:804: dpe 'gar bya btsal zhes rnyed du re bas 'tshol ba'i bya ba byed pa'i don dang /
NK102(ne)004:805: 'ga' shas su bya rtsol zhes 'bad brtson chen pos
NK102(ne)004:806: rtsol sgrub byed pa'i don te tshig gi brjod stangs
NK102(ne)004:807: mi 'dra ba gnyis su snang na'ang don la khyad
NK102(ne)004:808: par cang med / gang ltar yang /
NK102(ne)004:809: lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas lugs ye gdod ma nas
NK102(ne)004:810: ma bsgrubs par lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin de
NK102(ne)004:811: ni dper na me long gi mtshan nyid gsal la
NK102(ne)004:812: dag pa rang chas su yod pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:813: sgron me'i mtshan nyid 'od kyi snang ba rang chas su yod cing /
NK102(ne)004:814: mtshan nyid de dag dang mi ldan par me long dang sgron me ma yin pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:815: ye gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems de'i ngang du ma rdzogs pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:816: lhun gyis ma grub pa'i chos 'ga' yang med pas /
NK102(ne)004:817: da gzod sems pa 'du byed dang bcas pas dmigs bsam mtshan ma'i sgo nas bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:818: sngar med pa'i yon tan ci zhig kyang btsal du
NK102(ne)004:819: med pa lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid du bstan
NK102(ne)004:821: zhes spyir stangs su sgo gsum la g.yo sgyu sogs
NK102(ne)004:822: med pa bden zhing drang ba'am srong ba zhig la
NK102(ne)004:823: zer ba yin / 'on yang skabs 'gar rig byed klog pa'i ri shi'am drang srong dang /
NK102(ne)004:824: ston pa sangs rgyas la drang srong chen po zhes
NK102(ne)004:825: pa'i mtshan gyi bsnyad pa lta bu 'ga' re'ang snang
NK102(ne)004:827: zhes khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung ste
NK102(ne)004:828: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims kyi gzhi stegs so
NK102(ne)004:829: sor thar pa rigs brgyad bsnyen gnas dge bsnyen pha
NK102(ne)004:830: ma dang dge tshul pha ma dge slob ma dge
NK102(ne)004:831: slong pha ma kyi sdom pa gang rung la gnas
NK102(ne)004:833: ces phyi rol pa rnams kyi me lnga sogs la bsten pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:834: nang pa rnams kyis gso sbyong gi sdom par brten nas phyi dro'i kha zas bsnyung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:835: ngag gi smra brjod bsnyung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:836: yid kyi mi dge ba'i dran rtog bsnyung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:837: yid kyi mi dge ba'i dran rtog bsnyung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:838: rtag tu sbyong ba'i yon tan bcu gnyis la bsten cing /
NK102(ne)004:839: thos bsam sgom gsum gyi skabs gsum por sgo gsum
NK102(ne)004:840: gang la gang 'os pa'i dka' spyad hur thag gis
NK102(ne)004:841: byed pa ni / bod yul du yongs grags rje
NK102(ne)004:842: btsun mi la ras pa'i dka' thub kyi lo rgyus
NK102(ne)004:843: lta bu rnams la zer ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:845: ces yan lag dang nying lag du ma lhan cig
NK102(ne)004:846: tu tshogs pa'i phung po de la lus zhes bya
NK102(ne)004:847: la / de'ang 'bral zhing lus pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis lus kyi tha snyad byas pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:848: lha mi sogs so so'i lus sna tshogs su snang
NK102(ne)004:849: bas bdag gi lus zhes mngon par rtog cing zhen
NK102(ne)004:850: te / tha na rmi lam du'ang me chu g.yang
NK102(ne)004:851: sa dgra gcan sogs mthong ba'i tshe rang lus la
NK102(ne)004:852: gnod par dogs nas 'bros pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:853: sdug bsngal sna tshogs myong bar mthong ba de dag
NK102(ne)004:854: ni lus su rtog pa'i mngon zhen las byung zhing
NK102(ne)004:855: / de ni gnyis snang 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag tu 'dzin pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:856: dbye na gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK102(ne)004:857: chos kyi bdag gnyis su yod pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:859: zhes dbang po tshogs drug yul la mngon par zhen
NK102(ne)004:860: pa'i mthus kun nas nyon mongs pa'i las sna tshogs
NK102(ne)004:861: bskyed cing / las du ma bsags pa'i mthus 'khor
NK102(ne)004:862: ba mtha' med du 'khyams par 'gyur ba yin stabs
NK102(ne)004:863: bskyed cing / / snang yul la mngon par zhen
NK102(ne)004:864: pa ni khams gsum du 'khor ba'i rtsa ba dang
NK102(ne)004:865: bskyed cing / / / sgo gsum gyi kun spyod
NK102(ne)004:866: thams cad kyi nang nas nus pa che shos dang
NK102(ne)004:867: bskyed cing / / / / sngon byon dam pa
NK102(ne)004:868: rnams kyis mngon zhen las grol ba gdams pa'i yang
NK102(ne)004:869: snying du gsungs pa de 'dra'i gzhi rtsa gal chen
NK102(ne)004:872: pha dam pa sangs rgyas dus rabs 11rnams kyis gsungs pa'i zhal gdams rnams su /
NK102(ne)004:874: zhes pa'i tshig rkang 'di yongs grags yin pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:876: bla ma sa skya pa chen po kun dga' snying po dgung lo bcu gnyis bzhes pa'i tshe /
NK102(ne)004:877: 'phags pa 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi sgrub pa zla ba drug mdzad pas /
NK102(ne)004:878: dus gcig gi tshe 'od tshogs kyi dbus su rin
NK102(ne)004:879: po che'i khri zhig gi steng na rje btsun 'jam
NK102(ne)004:880: dbyangs dmar ser chos 'chad kyi phyag rgya can /
NK102(ne)004:881: bzang po'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK102(ne)004:882: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' gnyis g.yas g.yon du gnas pa mngon sum gzigs te gtso bo'i zhal nas /
NK102(ne)004:883: tshe 'di la zhen na chos pa min //
NK102(ne)004:884: khams gsum la zhen na nges 'byung min //
NK102(ne)004:885: bdag don la zhen na byang sems min //
NK102(ne)004:886: 'dzin pa byung na lta ba min //
NK102(ne)004:887: zhes gsungs pa'i don la dpyad pas /
NK102(ne)004:888: pha rol tu phyin pa'i lam gyi nyams len thams
NK102(ne)004:889: cad zhen pa bzhi dang bral ba'i blo sbyong du
NK102(ne)004:891: chos thams cad la nges shes khyad par can thob pa yin no //
NK102(ne)004:892: zhes gsungs pas mtshon ris su ma chad pa'i chos
NK102(ne)004:893: dang gdams pa thams cad kyi gnad ka ni zhen
NK102(ne)004:894: pa dang bral bar bstan to //
NK102(ne)004:895: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka byang chub chen po /
NK102(ne)004:896: zhes rgyu dang 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK102(ne)004:897: theg pa che chung gang zhig yin kyang rung rten
NK102(ne)004:898: cing 'brel te 'byung ba'i mtshan nyid du mthun par
NK102(ne)004:900: 'jig rten phyi nang gi dngos po 'di kun byed pos ma byas pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:901: rang bzhin las ma byung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:902: rgyu med pa las ma byung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:903: dus kyis bsgyur ba tsam zhig ma yin par /
NK102(ne)004:904: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel gyi mtshan nyid las grub cing /
NK102(ne)004:906: rgyu 'bras bu la ltos pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:908: rgyu rkyen lhan cig tu tshogs na 'bras bu skye la /
NK102(ne)004:909: ma tshogs na 'bras bu skye bar mi 'gyur bas rang grub ma yin /
NK102(ne)004:910: des na 'jig rten kun 'byung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:911: sdug bsngal gyi chos thams cad las 'das pa na /
NK102(ne)004:912: phung po ma lus pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su 'gyur bar bzhed la /
NK102(ne)004:913: rdzogs pa chen po'i skabs 'dir ni /
NK102(ne)004:914: ye gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems de'i ngang
NK102(ne)004:915: du lhun gyis ma grub pa'i chos ci zhig kyang
NK102(ne)004:916: med pas / rgyu 'bras kyis bsnyad pa'i chos kun kyang de'i ngang du rdzogs shing /
NK102(ne)004:917: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka byang chub chen po ste /
NK102(ne)004:918: ji ltar me long du gzugs brnyan mdzes mi mdzes ci rigs pa 'char na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:919: gsal dag me long gi ngang nyid de rang las mi 'da' ba ltar /
NK102(ne)004:920: byang chub sems kyi klong chen po der 'khor 'das
NK102(ne)004:921: kyis bsdus pa'i dag ma dag ci rigs pa zhig
NK102(ne)004:922: 'char na'ang / don du byang chub chen po'i rtsal
NK102(ne)004:923: dang rol par shar ba tsam las gzhan ma yin
NK102(ne)004:924: 'char na'ang / la / shar grol gnyis med mnyam
NK102(ne)004:925: pa chen po'i ngang nyid du gnas pa'i tshe na
NK102(ne)004:926: rgyu 'bras kyi chos las yongs su 'das shing /
NK102(ne)004:927: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka byang chub chen po ji ltar
NK102(ne)004:928: me long du gzugs brnyan sna tshogs su 'char ba
NK102(ne)004:929: de dag me long gi khyad chos sam yon tan
NK102(ne)004:930: du shar ba yin pa las /
NK102(ne)004:931: gzugs brnyan bzang ngan gyis me long la bde sdug
NK102(ne)004:932: gi tshor ba ci zhig kyang 'byin mi nus pa
NK102(ne)004:934: re zhig kun rdzogs kyi chos bla dwags su gnas pa na /
NK102(ne)004:935: ji ltar byis pas me long du shar ba'i gzugs brnyan la gzugs brnyan du ma shes shing /
NK102(ne)004:936: bden par zhen pa'i sgo nas spang len gyi byed
NK102(ne)004:937: rtsol la zhugs te bde sdug gi tshor ba ci
NK102(ne)004:938: rigs pa nyams su myong bas mtshon rgyu 'bras gnyis
NK102(ne)004:940: dge sdig blang dor gyi gnas la tshul bzhin du 'jug dgos pa 'di yin /
NK102(ne)004:942: ji ltar me long gi rang bzhin la 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' ba ltar /
NK102(ne)004:943: byang chub chen po don dam gshis kyi gnas lugs
NK102(ne)004:944: la rgyu 'bras kyis 'pho 'gyur ci'ang byed du med
NK102(ne)004:945: pas na rgyu 'bras gnyis ka byang chub chen po
NK102(ne)004:946: zhes pa'i brdas bsnyad pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:948: zhes nam mkha'i rang bzhin ni kun la khyab pa zhig yin na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:949: 'di dang 'adi'o zhes mtshan mar bzung du 'os pa ci zhig kyang mi mnga' ba ltar /
NK102(ne)004:950: gzhi gshis kyi gnas lugs byang chub chen po de ni nam mkha' ltar kun tu khyab na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:951: byed rtsol gyis legs pa'i cha dang du len pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:952: nyes pa'i cha spang ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:953: med pa gsar du bsgrub pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:954: yod pa gang zhig legs su gtang ba'am /
NK102(ne)004:955: 'phel rgyas byed pa sogs kyi byed las ci zhig dang yang ma 'brel ba ste /
NK102(ne)004:956: byed rtsol gang gis kyang 'pho 'gyur byed du med pa zhig yin /
NK102(ne)004:957: skabs 'dir nam mkha' zhes dper bstan pa de'ang kun tu khyab pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:958: dngos mtshan du ma grub pa stong pa'i cha nas
NK102(ne)004:959: mkha' zhes ye gzhi'i gnas lugs kyi cha shas tsam
NK102(ne)004:960: mtshon pa'i dper bkod pa las /
NK102(ne)004:961: gshis kyi gnas lugs yongs rdzogs mtshon pa'i dpe ni shes bya la mi srid pas /
NK102(ne)004:962: rdzogs pa chen po dpe las 'das pa zhes su grags pa de ga yin /
NK102(ne)004:964: ces lam nyams su len pa'i skabs kyi gdams pa rnams su ma bcos pa zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:965: 'dir bcos su med ces gsungs pa de dag don gcig pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:966: 'on kyang bcos su med ces pa'i tshig de dag
NK102(ne)004:967: gis ni gzhi gshis kyi gnas lugs snying po byang
NK102(ne)004:968: chub kyi sems / ngo bo stong pa /
NK102(ne)004:970: thugs rje 'gags med kyi ye shes sum ldan du
NK102(ne)004:971: bzhugs pa de nyid ji ltar yin pa la yin
NK102(ne)004:972: par shes nas grol bar 'gyur dgos pa las /
NK102(ne)004:973: med pa la yod par sgro 'dogs pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:975: legs su bcos pa sogs dmigs bsam byed rtsol gang
NK102(ne)004:976: zhig gis kyang bcos su med pa zhig yin stabs
NK102(ne)004:977: / ye gzhi'i gnas lugs bcos su med par bstan la /
NK102(ne)004:978: ma bcos pa zhes pa'i tshig de dag gis ni
NK102(ne)004:979: lam dus su ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag
NK102(ne)004:980: pa'i tshe blo'i 'du byed kyis ma bcos pa /
NK102(ne)004:982: rig tsam pa de ka'i ngang du 'jog dgos par bstan /
NK102(ne)004:983: tshig 'gros de gnyis kyis gzhi gshis kyi yin lugs bstan pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:984: ting nge 'dzin la 'jog stangs bstan pa'i khyad shin
NK102(ne)004:985: tu phra ba zhig las don la mi 'dra ba
NK102(ne)004:988: zhes dpe rnying 'ga' shas su brdal ba zhes pa'am
NK102(ne)004:989: gdal ba zhes kyang gsal ba de dag gi don
NK102(ne)004:992: nam rgyun du khyab brdal lam /
NK102(ne)004:993: khyab gdal zhes pa dang don gcig pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:994: de yang skye 'gro kun gyis rgyu nyon mongs pa lnga'am lhan cig pa dang drug bsags pa las /
NK102(ne)004:995: 'bras bu 'gro ba rigs drug gi las snang 'byung zhing /
NK102(ne)004:996: las kyi 'bras bu smin nas khams gsum 'khor bar
NK102(ne)004:997: mtha' med du 'khor zhing 'khyams pa de la ma
NK102(ne)004:998: dag pa'i snang ba zhes bya /
NK102(ne)004:999: las snang de sbyangs pa'am bsgyur ba na dag pa'i snang ba 'char zhing /
NK102(ne)004:1000: dag ma dag gi snang ba de kun ni /
NK102(ne)004:1001: ji ltar gsal zhing dag pa'i me long gi ngogs
NK102(ne)004:1002: su rten 'brel bzang ngan gyi snang ba sna tshogs
NK102(ne)004:1004: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes sum ldan byang chub kyi
NK102(ne)004:1005: sems dam pa de'i klong du gnyis snang gi chos
NK102(ne)004:1006: cir yang 'char du rung ba ste /
NK102(ne)004:1007: snang srid snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos ma lus
NK102(ne)004:1008: pa snying po byang chub kyi sems su rdzogs shing
NK102(ne)004:1009: / byang chub kyi sems las 'das pa'i chos ci zhig kyang med la /
NK102(ne)004:1010: de dang 'dra ba byang chub kyi sems kyis ma
NK102(ne)004:1011: khyab pa ni 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos ci
NK102(ne)004:1013: bdal ba chen po zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1014: byang chub kyi sems kyis khyab par bdal ba'i bdal
NK102(ne)004:1015: ba chen po zhes pa de'ang byang chub kyi sems
NK102(ne)004:1016: kyis byed pa po ltar chos kun bkod pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:1017: 'du byed gang yang rung bas dmigs mtshan can du bskrun pa'i don ni min la /
NK102(ne)004:1018: 'khor 'das gnyis snang gi chos ma lus pa byang
NK102(ne)004:1019: chub sems kyi rtsal dang rol pa las 'gags med
NK102(ne)004:1020: kyi snang char shar ba dper na /
NK102(ne)004:1021: me long dwangs pa'i ngogasasu rten 'brel gyi chos ci rigs 'char chog pa dang 'dra ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1023: zhes rang rig pa'i gnas lugs rjen gcer bud de
NK102(ne)004:1024: gshis rnal ma'i gnas lugs bya btsal dang bral ba
NK102(ne)004:1025: de nyid mngon du byed pa'am rtogs pa na /
NK102(ne)004:1026: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun rang rig pa'i gdangs dang /
NK102(ne)004:1028: rtsal du shar ba las ma 'das shing /
NK102(ne)004:1029: kun kyang ye nas ji ltar yin pa'i gnas lugs
NK102(ne)004:1030: yongs su rtogs pas ye shes dam pa la mnga'
NK102(ne)004:1032: de yang gzhi gnas kyi ye shes ngo bo stong pa /
NK102(ne)004:1034: thugs rje 'gags med du bzhugs pa'i gnas lugs de
NK102(ne)004:1035: nyid gshis rang thog tu ji ltar bar rtogs shing
NK102(ne)004:1036: / lam dus su gnas pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1041: bde ba gsum po nyams su myong ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1042: nam zhig na de kun mnyam rjes ris med kyi
NK102(ne)004:1043: ting 'dzin chen po'i khor yug tu yongs su bzlums
NK102(ne)004:1044: pas / 'bras dus su chos kyi sku dang /
NK102(ne)004:1045: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK102(ne)004:1046: sprul pa'i sku rnams mngon du gyur te /
NK102(ne)004:1047: ji ltar mkha' klong du nyi ma 'char ba na
NK102(ne)004:1048: mtha' yas pa'i 'od zer gyi phung po dus gcig
NK102(ne)004:1051: ji snyed par mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis mtshon mtha'
NK102(ne)004:1052: yas pa'i lhun grub kyi ye shes yon tan gyi
NK102(ne)004:1053: tshogs rnams 'gogs med du mngon par gsal ba yin
NK102(ne)004:1055: zhes rdzogs pa chen po lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK102(ne)004:1058: yid kyi dmigs bsam la sogs pa'i rtsol ba thams
NK102(ne)004:1059: cad las yongs su 'das pa'am bral ba zhig ste
NK102(ne)004:1060: / rdzogs chen sems sde'i lugs su byas na /
NK102(ne)004:1061: bsam gtan gyi rim pa bzhi'i sgo nas bya rtsol
NK102(ne)004:1062: dang bral ba lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK102(ne)004:1064: rdzogs chen klong sde'i lugs su byas na /
NK102(ne)004:1065: brda bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi rim pas bya rtsol dang
NK102(ne)004:1066: bral ba dbyer med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gzhol
NK102(ne)004:1067: ba dang / rdzogs chen man ngag sde'i lugs su byas na /
NK102(ne)004:1068: cog bzhag rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas rig pa'i rang
NK102(ne)004:1069: ngo bskyang zhing sems las 'das pa'i ye shes dam
NK102(ne)004:1070: pa de nyid mngon du byed pas na bya rtsol
NK102(ne)004:1072: nam mkhar 'gyur ba'i gzhi ma yin /
NK102(ne)004:1073: zhes nam mkha' ni ye gzhi snying po byang chub sems kyi mtshon dpe zhig te /
NK102(ne)004:1074: des ni stong zhing kun la khyab pa'i bdag nyid du bstan pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1075: nam mkha' 'gyur ba zhes pa ni snang sems 'dres pa'i don te /
NK102(ne)004:1076: sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos kun byang chub sems kyi rtsal dang rol pa las ma 'das na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:1077: glo bur gyi sgrib pa sprin dang 'dra ba des /
NK102(ne)004:1078: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs nyi ma'i snying po dang 'dra ba de yongs su bsgribs nas /
NK102(ne)004:1079: gnyis snang gi 'khrul rtog sna tshogs pa'i 'du byed
NK102(ne)004:1080: kyis 'khor ba lu gu rgyud du 'khyams pa de'i
NK102(ne)004:1081: rang mtshang rjen par rig nas /
NK102(ne)004:1082: kun khyab bdal ba chen po nam mkha' dang 'dra
NK102(ne)004:1083: ba de'i ngang nyid du gnyis dbyer med par 'gyur
NK102(ne)004:1084: ba de'i gazhi'am rtsa ba ni rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK102(ne)004:1085: zab mo de kho na nyid yin par bstan /
NK102(ne)004:1087: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin de ni ye nas
NK102(ne)004:1088: nam mkha' ltar kun khyab stong pa'i rang bzhin du
NK102(ne)004:1090: da gzod nam mkha'i rang bzhin du 'gyur ba'i gazhi'am /
NK102(ne)004:1091: bsgrub bya'i gzhi gang zhig kyang ma yin pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:1092: rang bzhin nam mkhar gnas pa la //
NK102(ne)004:1093: nam mkhar 'gyur ba'i gzhi ma yin //
NK102(ne)004:1094: zhes pa'i tshig rkang 'di gnyis kyis yin pa sgrub pa'i sgra dang /
NK102(ne)004:1095: ma yin pa dgag pa'i sgra ste /
NK102(ne)004:1096: tshig 'gros kyi dbang du byas na /
NK102(ne)004:1097: snga mas gzhi ma ste gzhi rtsa yin pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1098: phyi mas ma yin te nam mkha'i rang bzhin du
NK102(ne)004:1099: 'gyur ba'i gzhi rtsa gang zhig kyang ma yin pa
NK102(ne)004:1100: bcas don gnyis dus gcig tu bstan /
NK102(ne)004:1102: ces thun mong theg pa'i lugs su /
NK102(ne)004:1103: kun gzhi ni bag chags kyi gzhi yul gyi don tsam rig pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:1104: skad cig ma du ma mthud pa'i rgyun brtan pa zhig la ngos 'dzin pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1109: rgyu'i ngo bor gyur pa gnyis yod /
NK102(ne)004:1110: ngo bo ni sgrib la lung ma bstan pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1112: dmigs pa mi gsal ba snod bcud rgya chen po la dmigs pa zhig yin /
NK102(ne)004:1113: des na tshogs bdun 'khor bcas rang gi rgyun las mi skye ste /
NK102(ne)004:1114: rigs 'dra phyi ma grub pa'i bag chags kun gzhi
NK102(ne)004:1115: la bgos te bum pa'i grib ma ltar kun gzhi'i
NK102(ne)004:1116: skad cig re re la skye ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1118: 'dus byas kyi dge mi dge lung ma bstan rnam shes dang bcas pa'i rten byed pas /
NK102(ne)004:1119: bag chags sna tshogs pa'i kun gzhi zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1120: skabs 'dir bstan gyi kun gzhi chos nyid ni /
NK102(ne)004:1121: khams bde gshegs snying po rang bzhin rnam dag gi
NK102(ne)004:1122: myang 'das 'dus ma byas pa'i yon tan dang ngo
NK102(ne)004:1123: bo nyid kyis mi 'bral bas don gyi kun gzhi
NK102(ne)004:1124: zhes su grags pa de dang don gcig pa yin
NK102(ne)004:1125: / sems nyid nam mkha' byang chub dbyings /
NK102(ne)004:1126: zhes sems ni kun tu rtog pa gnyis 'dzin gyi gazhi'am rtsa bar gyur pa de nyid yin la /
NK102(ne)004:1127: de ni dper na me long du mdzes mi mdzes
NK102(ne)004:1128: kyi gzugs brnyan sna tshogs pa 'char ba'i gzugs brnyan
NK102(ne)004:1129: dang 'dra la / sems kyi ngo bo nyid 'di zhes ngos bzung du med pa /
NK102(ne)004:1130: ma brtags ma dpyad par kun rtog sna tshogs pa bden bden dang /
NK102(ne)004:1131: yod yod 'dra ba'i zol gyis 'gags med du 'phro la /
NK102(ne)004:1132: brtags shing dpyad pa na ci'ang rnyed du med pa'i
NK102(ne)004:1133: snying po ka dag stong pa nyid nam mkha'i dbyings
NK102(ne)004:1135: thun mong theg pa'i lugs su ches grags pa'i sems nyid ces bya ba de la /
NK102(ne)004:1136: gsang ba sngags kyi lugs su phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK102(ne)004:1138: rnam kun mchog ldan sogs kyi tha snyad mi 'dra ba du mar grags shing /
NK102(ne)004:1139: a ti yo ga'i skabs 'dir rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK102(ne)004:1143: rang byung ye shes sogs su grags pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1144: de lta bu'i byang chub kyis sems de'i dbyings ni /
NK102(ne)004:1145: ye gzhi gshis kyi klong chen po ji ltar yin
NK102(ne)004:1146: pa de'i ngang nyid la tha snyad de skad du
NK102(ne)004:1149: zhes ji bzhin ba'i chos zhes bya ba la ji bzhin ba zhig tu dmigs nas btsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1150: de kho na ces pa la de kho na nyid cig tu dmigs nas btsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1151: gza' gtad med pa la gza' gtad dang bral ba'i chos shig tu dmigs nas btsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1152: lhun gyis grub par lhun gyis grub pa'i chos shig tu dmigs nas btsal ba sogs /
NK102(ne)004:1153: btsal sems dang bcas pa de ni re dog gi mtha' las ma 'das pas /
NK102(ne)004:1154: btsal sems dang bral ba de ni snying po byang
NK102(ne)004:1155: chub kyi sems dam pa mngon du 'gyur ba'i gazhi'am
NK102(ne)004:1157: byang chub sgrub pa'i gzhi ma yin /
NK102(ne)004:1158: btsal sems dang yongs su bral bas snying po byang
NK102(ne)004:1159: chub sems kyi dbyings chen po ji ltar yin pa
NK102(ne)004:1160: la yin par shes pa'i ngang nyid du gnas pa
NK102(ne)004:1161: de ni byang chub chen po mngon du sgrub pa'i
NK102(ne)004:1162: gzhi ma'am rtsa ba zhig te /
NK102(ne)004:1163: gzhi rtsa de dang bral ba ni ji ltar dbul
NK102(ne)004:1164: po'i sngas stegs pha lam gyis byas te mi tshe
NK102(ne)004:1166: rang gi sngas su pha lam yod par ma shes
NK102(ne)004:1167: pa'i rkyen gyis dbul phongs kyi sdug bsngal yun ring
NK102(ne)004:1168: du myong ba'i mtha' bkres shing skom pas nyes te
NK102(ne)004:1169: tshe 'phos pa'i dpe dang 'dra ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1171: sems kyi de kho na nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra
NK102(ne)004:1172: ba de ni ye gdod ma nas byang chub chen
NK102(ne)004:1174: sngon med kyi byang chub gsar du sgrub pa'i gzhi ci zhig ma yin pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:1175: sems nyid nam mkha' byang chub dbyings //
NK102(ne)004:1176: byang chub sgrub pa'i gzhi ma yin //
NK102(ne)004:1177: zhes pa'i tshig rkang 'di gnyis kyis ni yin pa sgrub sgra dang /
NK102(ne)004:1178: ma yin pa dgag sgra'i don gnyis cha dus gcig tu bstan par shes so //
NK102(ne)004:1179: gzhi rtsa myed pa'i sems nyid /
NK102(ne)004:1180: ces sems ni rnam par rtog pa sna tshogs skyed mkhan 'di yin la /
NK102(ne)004:1181: rnam rtog las gzhan du sems zhes bya ba ngos 'dzin du rung ba ci zhig kyang ma mchis /
NK102(ne)004:1182: rnam rtog gi rang ngor bltas tsa na /
NK102(ne)004:1183: 'di nyid gang nas skyes pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1185: gang du phyin pa'i gazhi'am rtsa ba 'di yin zhes ngos bzung thub pa 'ga' yang med pas /
NK102(ne)004:1186: gzhi rtsa myed pa zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1187: de ltar ngos 'dzin du med cing /
NK102(ne)004:1188: gang zhig rnyed pa de ni stong zhing bdag med pa tsam las gzhan med na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:1189: kun rtog ni ma rnyed pa de ka'i ngang nas 'gags med du yang yang shar ba ste /
NK102(ne)004:1190: de lta bu'i ngo bo stong la rang bzhin gsal ba /
NK102(ne)004:1191: thugs rje 'gags pa med pa zhig mngon sum myong
NK102(ne)004:1192: bas grub pa'i bdag nyid 'di la snying po byang
NK102(ne)004:1193: chub sems kyi de kho na nyid ces pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:1194: de'i tshig sna bsdus pa'i tshul gyis sems nyid ces su grags pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1196: zhes 'di ni yang dag pa'i gnas la rmongs pa'i dpe zhig te /
NK102(ne)004:1197: su zhig gis me dang chu dgra ru shes shing /
NK102(ne)004:1198: de'i tshul la mkhas par rloms na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:1199: dngos po'i rang gshis kyi gnas tshul mes chu gsod pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:1200: chus me gsod pa'i nges shes ji bzhin ma rnyed cing /
NK102(ne)004:1201: me gsad pa'i phyir du chu 'khyer nas /
NK102(ne)004:1202: chu de me'i steng du 'pho nas me gsad dgos rgyu yin pa la /
NK102(ne)004:1203: me 'pho zhing chu gsod pa'i bya ba la zhugs
NK102(ne)004:1204: pa lta bu yun ring gi ngal ba ci 'dra
NK102(ne)004:1206: dgos don 'grub pa'i dus med par mtshon pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1208: mes chu gsod pa'i nges shes kyi blo gros tsam yod na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:1209: rtag tu g.yeng bas gzhan dbang du gyur te /
NK102(ne)004:1210: nam zhig me gsad dgos pa'i dus la babs pa na /
NK102(ne)004:1211: me 'pho ste chu gsod pa'i bya ba byed pa lta bu go don gnyis dang ldan pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1212: ri dwags smrig rgyu snyog pa /
NK102(ne)004:1213: zhes mya ngam gyis gdung ba'i thang chen du gnas
NK102(ne)004:1214: pa'i ri dwags rnams kyis chu btung bar 'dod de
NK102(ne)004:1216: rgyang ring nas smrig rgyu mthong ba de chur 'khrul
NK102(ne)004:1217: te ngal ba chen pos yun ring du bgrod na'ang
NK102(ne)004:1218: / ri dwags rnams phar phar phyin pa na smrig
NK102(ne)004:1219: rgyu'ang phar phar phyin te slebs pa'i skabs mi 'byung
NK102(ne)004:1220: / / de ltar na'ang 'khrul rtog la yid ches che zhing /
NK102(ne)004:1221: skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis chu la re che bas
NK102(ne)004:1222: ngal ba khyad du bsad de smrig rgyu'i rjes su
NK102(ne)004:1223: snyegs pa ltar / dus ring du sgo gsum ngal
NK102(ne)004:1224: ba chen pos rtsol sgrub ci 'dra zhig byas na'ang
NK102(ne)004:1225: lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid chen po las gzhan
NK102(ne)004:1226: gang zhig kyang rnyed du med par bstan pa yin
NK102(ne)004:1227: snyegs pa ltar / / skye dang bral ba'i byang chub /
NK102(ne)004:1230: 'gag pa gsum ni dus gsum gyi cha la lta ba'i tshul zhig yin la /
NK102(ne)004:1231: de'ang thog mar ma skyes par gnas pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1233: kun gyi thog mar skye ba bstan pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1234: de bas na ye gdod ma nas skye ba dang
NK102(ne)004:1235: bral ba'am skye ma myong ba'i snying po byang chub
NK102(ne)004:1236: kyi sems te / nam rgyun du skye med ces
NK102(ne)004:1237: pa'i tha snyad yongs su grags pa de dang don
NK102(ne)004:1238: kyi sems te / gcig cing / skye med du rtogs pas 'gag med dang /
NK102(ne)004:1239: gnas med yin pa'ang rang shugs su rtogs thub pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1241: zhes ye gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems de
NK102(ne)004:1242: la rgyu dang 'bras bur grub pa ci zhig kyang
NK102(ne)004:1243: ma mchis pas rdzogs pa chen po rgyu 'bras las
NK102(ne)004:1245: kun rdzob rgyu 'bras su bsnyad pa de dag kyang
NK102(ne)004:1246: snying po byang chub sems kyi rtsal du shar ba
NK102(ne)004:1247: tsam las gzhan ma yin tshul gong du tshig 'grel
NK102(ne)004:1248: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka byang chub chen po zhes pa'i
NK102(ne)004:1249: skabs su gsal bar bshad pa ltar yin /
NK102(ne)004:1251: ces sdig pa ni mi dge ba bcu ste /
NK102(ne)004:1252: lus kyi sgo nas gzhan gyi srog gcod pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1254: 'dod pas log par g.yems pa gsum dang /
NK102(ne)004:1255: ngag gi sgo nas rdzu smra ba /
NK102(ne)004:1259: yid kyi sgo nas brnab sems skye ba /
NK102(ne)004:1261: log par lta ba gsum bcas bcu po 'di dag yin /
NK102(ne)004:1262: de dag la ji mi snyam pas 'chol nyog tu
NK102(ne)004:1263: spyad pas bden don mthong bar gegs byed cing mthong
NK102(ne)004:1264: du mi ster ba'i sdig par 'gyur zhing /
NK102(ne)004:1265: dge ba ni legs pa'i phyogs su 'dren pas dge ba ste /
NK102(ne)004:1266: gong gsal las lam bcu po de dag las bzlog
NK102(ne)004:1267: cing dran shes kyis yongs su 'tsho ba la dge
NK102(ne)004:1268: ba bcu zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1270: zhes 'gro ba rigs drug tu dbye ba'i tshe /
NK102(ne)004:1271: dbang po'i khyad par gyis mtho ba'i gnas ris lha dang /
NK102(ne)004:1274: de dag las dbang po'i khyad par gyis dman pa dmyal ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1276: dud 'gro'i 'jig rten gsum la ngan song gsum du grags pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:1277: mtho ba ni bsod nams dge ba'i tshogs las byung ba'i las dang /
NK102(ne)004:1279: dbang po'i bye brag rnams ngan song gi gnas la
NK102(ne)004:1280: ltos na ches mtho ba'i gnas ris su song bas
NK102(ne)004:1281: na mtho ris zhes su grags pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1283: zhes gnas skabs su 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal ji snyed pa rnams dang /
NK102(ne)004:1284: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal bzod par dka' ba rnams las thar ba'i thar pa zhig dang /
NK102(ne)004:1285: mthar thug tu srid pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1286: zhi ba'i mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas pa'i thar pa
NK102(ne)004:1287: dam pa byang chub chen po mngon du 'gyur ba
NK102(ne)004:1288: ste / mya ngan las yongs su 'das pa zhes
NK102(ne)004:1289: su grags pa bcas thar pa'i gtso bo rigs gnyis
NK102(ne)004:1290: ste / yod pa yin / yongs kyi myed /
NK102(ne)004:1291: ces snying po byang chub kyi sems de nyid rgyu 'bras su grub pa 'ga' yang med cing /
NK102(ne)004:1297: 'khor ba zhes bya dngos mtshan du grub pa 'ga' yang med pa lta ci /
NK102(ne)004:1298: ming tsam du'ang ma grub pas yongs kyis med ces bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1299: de ni a ti yo ga'i skabs tsam du ma zad /
NK102(ne)004:1300: shes rab snying po las kyang /
NK102(ne)004:1305: zhes gsungs pas kyang shes thub pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1306: de ltar na chad par lta bar mi 'gyur ram snyam du'ang mi bsam ste /
NK102(ne)004:1307: snying po byang chub kyi sems de nyid rgyu 'bras
NK102(ne)004:1308: su grub pa 'ga' yang myed par bshad pa las
NK102(ne)004:1309: / byang chub kyi sems la rtsal dang rol pa med ces bshad pa ma yin /
NK102(ne)004:1310: dper na me long zhes pa de nyid gzugs brnyan ma yin zhes bshad pa las /
NK102(ne)004:1311: me long du gzugs brnyan med ces pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:1312: me long la gzugs brnyan 'char nus gsal dag rnyogs
NK102(ne)004:1313: pa med pa'i yon tan med ces bshad pa ma
NK102(ne)004:1316: ces lde'u mig ces kyang bya ba 'di ni sgo lcags 'byed byed cig yin la /
NK102(ne)004:1317: sgo lcags 'byed par med du mi rung ba ni lde mig yin pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1318: de med na khang pa'i nang du yod pa'i bang
NK102(ne)004:1319: mdzod sogs mngon sum du mthong ba'i skabs mi yong
NK102(ne)004:1320: bas / lde mig la dgos pa khyad can zhig yod nges pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:1321: a ti yo ga'i rgyud lung man ngag gi skor
NK102(ne)004:1322: rgya che zhing grangs mang ba de kun la blta
NK102(ne)004:1323: ba'i go skabs 'byed byed lde mig dang 'dra ba'i
NK102(ne)004:1324: man ngag bla na med pa zhig yin par bstan
NK102(ne)004:1325: / man ngag bla na med pa /
NK102(ne)004:1326: zhes bzo 'phrul gyi 'khor lo'i gnad ka gsal bar shes shing /
NK102(ne)004:1327: de'i gnad du gcun shes na 'phrul 'khor gyi byed las ji bzhin 'byung ba ltar /
NK102(ne)004:1328: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud dang /
NK102(ne)004:1330: gdams pa rgya che zhing grangs mang ba de kun
NK102(ne)004:1331: gyi rtsa gnad gcig tu 'dus pa'i man ngag a
NK102(ne)004:1332: ti yo ga'i dgongs pa bla na med pa de
NK102(ne)004:1333: nyid 'dir nyung ngu'i tshig gis mtshon par bstan /
NK102(ne)004:1335: gsang ba'i gdan nye bar bsdus pa'i dpe zhig te /
NK102(ne)004:1336: ji ltar bya rog gi 'bru rigs nyung tsam zhig rgum bur btus te /
NK102(ne)004:1337: slad nas longs su spyod pa'i ched du /
NK102(ne)004:1338: kho rang gi yid khar babs pa'i sa gnas gang rung zhig tu sbas nas bzhag pa ltar /
NK102(ne)004:1339: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud lung man ngag gi bka' bstan rgya chen po rgyal po'i bang mdzod dam /
NK102(ne)004:1340: ston kha'i 'bru zhing dang 'dra ba de dag las
NK102(ne)004:1341: phyi rabs gdul bya'i ched du snying po'i don bsdus
NK102(ne)004:1342: pa'i tshig tshogs nyung ngu bya rog gi rgum bu
NK102(ne)004:1343: ltar / rgyas spros dang bral ba'i dpe chung ngu zhig gi don yin /
NK102(ne)004:1345: zhes legs sbyar du bud+d+ha gup+ta zhes su grags shing /
NK102(ne)004:1346: dpe rnying mang zhig tu ni 'bu ta kuka ta
NK102(ne)004:1347: zhes par snang ba de ni phal cher de skabs
NK102(ne)004:1348: su mtshan gyi sgra ji bzhin grags pa de nyid
NK102(ne)004:1349: thad kar yi ger bkod pa'i lugs shig yin pa
NK102(ne)004:1350: smos ma dgos / mtshan gyi sgra de'ang phal cher
NK102(ne)004:1351: o rgyan gyi sgra gdangs las drangs pa zhig yin
NK102(ne)004:1352: srid pa'ang a ti yo ga'i rgyud lung phal mo
NK102(ne)004:1353: che o rgyan gyi skad nas bod skad du bsgyur
NK102(ne)004:1354: ba'i tshul bee ro'i rgyud 'bum las gsal ba de
NK102(ne)004:1356: sbas pa'i rgum chung gi dpe 'di dang /
NK102(ne)004:1357: bsam gtan mig sgron gyi phyi mo'i dpe rnams su
NK102(ne)004:1358: 'bu ta kuka ta zhes mtshan gyi sgra thad kar
NK102(ne)004:1359: bkod pa gsal bar snang ba 'dis kyang gzhung 'di
NK102(ne)004:1360: dag gi phyi mo'i dpe ni shin tu rnying ma
NK102(ne)004:1361: zhig yin pa gsal bar bstan pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1365: skabs 'gar yongs su rnal 'byor zhes kyang grags pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:1366: mtshan 'di ni lhun grub rdzogs pa chen po'i mtshan thun mong ma yin pa zhig yin /
NK102(ne)004:1367: sngags rnying ma'i lugs su theg pa rim pa dgu ru grags pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:1368: 'jig rten lha mi'i theg pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1370: byang sems theg pa ste rgyu'i theg pa gsum dang /
NK102(ne)004:1373: yo ga ste sngags phyi pa'i theg pa gsum dang /
NK102(ne)004:1374: ma h+aa yo ga'am rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK102(ne)004:1375: a nu yo ga'am shin tu rnal 'byor dang /
NK102(ne)004:1376: a ti yo ga'am yongs su rnal 'byor te sngags
NK102(ne)004:1377: nang pa'am rnal 'byor bla na med pa gsum bcas
NK102(ne)004:1378: theg pa rim pa dgu ru phye srol yod /
NK102(ne)004:1379: rnal 'byor bla na med par grags pa'i ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK102(ne)004:1380: a nu yo ga de gnyis ni sgyur lam gyi gtso bo dag yin la /
NK102(ne)004:1381: de dag kyang gtso che'i dbang du byas na ma
NK102(ne)004:1382: h+aa yo ga ni sgyur lam rim gyis pa ste
NK102(ne)004:1383: / de'i mthar thug la phyag rgya chen po zhes bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1384: a nu yo ga ni sgyur lam rim gyis ma yin pa ste /
NK102(ne)004:1385: de'i mthar thug la rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1386: a nu yo ga'i mthar thug la rdzogs chen du grags pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK102(ne)004:1387: lugs der thog ma nyid nas lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid du shes shing /
NK102(ne)004:1388: gdod nas rnam par dag pa lha dang lha mo'i
NK102(ne)004:1389: dkyil 'khor ji ltar yin pa la yin par shes
NK102(ne)004:1390: pas skad cig nyid du gsal 'debs pa'i sgyur lam
NK102(ne)004:1391: rim gyis ma yin pas lam nyams su len zhing
NK102(ne)004:1392: / de la brten nas lhun grub rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor la gzhol ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1393: de ltar na'ang de'i mthar thug rdzogs pa chen po yin gyis /
NK102(ne)004:1394: theg pa dngos ni a nu yo ga sgyur lam
NK102(ne)004:1395: gyi theg pa zhig yin pa las a ti yo
NK102(ne)004:1397: de'i rgyu mtshan gyis a nu yo ga dang /
NK102(ne)004:1398: a ti yo ga zhes bya ba'i theg rim mi 'dra ba gnyis su byung ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1400: rang grol gyi theg pa gnyis kyi khyad par yang gzhi rtsa de nas byung ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1401: byang chub kyi sems kyi lung /
NK102(ne)004:1402: zhes ye gzhi snying po byang chub kyi sems de
NK102(ne)004:1403: nyid gzhi lam 'bras bu'i gnas skabs so so'i yin
NK102(ne)004:1404: lugs ji bzhin bstan pa'i rgyud dang /
NK102(ne)004:1405: rgyud kyi rtsa gnad gal che'i grangs thor bur btus
NK102(ne)004:1406: shing lhan cig tu bsdebs pa'i lung rgyas pa rdzogs
NK102(ne)004:1407: pa chen po byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal
NK102(ne)004:1409: bsdus pa rdzogs chen sems sde snga 'gyur lnga'i grangs
NK102(ne)004:1410: sogs mang du bzhugs pa de rnams la sems kyi
NK102(ne)004:1411: lung zhes su grags pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1413: ces rdzogs pa chen po bya rtsol dang bral ba'i
NK102(ne)004:1414: gdams pa zab mo 'di ni gdul bya blo yang
NK102(ne)004:1415: rab rnams kyi don du byon par yongs su grags
NK102(ne)004:1417: rdzogs pa chen po nyams su len pa la /
NK102(ne)004:1418: gnas lugs kyi don rtogs nas nyams su len dgos kyis /
NK102(ne)004:1419: dmigs pa sems kyi 'du byed kyis lha bsgom pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1421: gzhan yang bde gshegs la mchod bstod 'bul ba /
NK102(ne)004:1422: phyag skor la 'bad pa sogs kyi dge sbyor ci 'dra zhig bgyis na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:1423: de dag rdzogs pa chen po'i lam stegs dge ba'i
NK102(ne)004:1424: tshogs tsam las a ti yo ga'am rdzogs pa chen
NK102(ne)004:1425: po'i nyams len du mi 'gyur zhing /
NK102(ne)004:1426: dge ba'i tshogs bsags pa tsam gyis snying po byung
NK102(ne)004:1427: chub sems kyi gnas lugs dam pa de mngon du
NK102(ne)004:1428: 'gyur ba shin tu nas kyang dka' ba yin /
NK102(ne)004:1429: gnas lugs kyi don rtogs par dbang po mchog ldan zhig nges par du yin dgos /
NK102(ne)004:1430: dbang po mchog ldan nam blo yang rab ces pa de grub pa thob pa'am /
NK102(ne)004:1431: sa thob pa'i sems dpa' zhig yin dgos pa'i nges pa med cing /
NK102(ne)004:1432: grub pa thob pa la lam gyi dgos pa'ang med pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1433: blo yang rab kyi don ni /
NK102(ne)004:1434: gdul bya su'ang rung ba de'i rgyud la dad brtson
NK102(ne)004:1435: dran pa ting 'dzin shes rab kyi dbang po rnams
NK102(ne)004:1437: 'ga' zhig ma tshang ba de dag kyang dran dang
NK102(ne)004:1438: shes bzhin gyi sgo nas tshang bar bsgrub shes shing
NK102(ne)004:1439: nus pa de 'dra ba zhig la go dgos pa
NK102(ne)004:1441: zhes gzhung 'dis bstan bya'i don ji snyed cig yod pa de kun gyi sdom tshig gi don te /
NK102(ne)004:1442: sgo zhes pa ni bshad bya'i sgo mi 'dra ba'i rigs ji snyed yod pa de rnams yin la /
NK102(ne)004:1443: gtsigs zhes pa ni brda rnying par gtsigs su che ste gal che ba'am /
NK102(ne)004:1444: gnad che ba'i don la 'jug cing /
NK102(ne)004:1445: 'dir bstan gyi don snying ni gnad che'i rigs lhan
NK102(ne)004:1446: du sdom pa phal cher deng dus kyi tha snyad
NK102(ne)004:1447: du grags che ba sa bcad ces pa dang 'dra
NK102(ne)004:1450: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:1451: me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:1452: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:1453: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK102(ne)004:1454: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te ye shes lngar bshad cing /
NK102(ne)004:1455: skabs 'dir ye shes lnga'i khyad gzhi rang byung gi
NK102(ne)004:1456: ye shes ni ji ltar 'od zer gang las 'phro
NK102(ne)004:1457: ba'i gzhi nyi ma'i snying po dang 'dra ba de
NK102(ne)004:1458: nyid ji bzhin du rtogs pa'i tshe rtogs pa'i ye
NK102(ne)004:1460: de nyid kyi khyad chos ye shes rnam pa lnga
NK102(ne)004:1461: dang bcas par ye shes drug gi brdas bsnyad pa
NK102(ne)004:1462: yin / che ba rnam pa lnga /
NK102(ne)004:1463: zhes gzhung 'di'i bstan don che ba rnam pa lnga ste /
NK102(ne)004:1464: 1kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin che ba /
NK102(ne)004:1465: 2byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin gyi che ba /
NK102(ne)004:1466: 3byang chub sems kyi dpe mi dmigs pa'i che ba /
NK102(ne)004:1467: 4kun gzhi mkha' dbyings rnam par dag pa'i che ba /
NK102(ne)004:1468: 5byang chub kyi sems gol sgrib dang bral ba'i che ba'o //
NK102(ne)004:1469: de kho na ni yin pa rnam gsum /
NK102(ne)004:1470: zhes1 sems nyid kyi rang bzhin nam mkha' ltar 'gyur med yin pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:1471: rang bzhin nam mkhar gnas pa la //
NK102(ne)004:1472: nam mkhar 'gyur ba'i gzhi ma yin //
NK102(ne)004:1473: zhes pa'i tshig rkang gnyis kyis bstan pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1474: 2sems nyid byang chub sems kyi dbyings yin pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:1475: sems nyid nam mkha' byang chub dbyings //
NK102(ne)004:1476: byang chub sgrub pa'i gzhi ma yin //
NK102(ne)004:1477: zhes pa'i tshig rkang gnyis kyis bstan pa dang /
NK102(ne)004:1478: 3sems nyid la gzhi rtsa med pas nam mkha' dang 'dra ba yin pa ni /
NK102(ne)004:1479: gzhi rtsa myed pa'i sems nyid la //
NK102(ne)004:1480: btsal bas myi rnyed nam mkha' 'dra //
NK102(ne)004:1481: zhes pa'i tshig rkang gnyis kyis bstan pa yin /
NK102(ne)004:1483: zhes snying po byang chub kyi sems su ma 'dus
NK102(ne)004:1484: pa'am byang chub kyi sems kyis ma khyab pa'i chos
NK102(ne)004:1486: kun la khyab cing dngos mtshan du ma grub pa'i stong pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK102(ne)004:1487: snying po byang chub kyi sems 'di zhes gang gis kyang mtshon du med cing /
NK102(ne)004:1488: de'ang gzung 'dzin gnyis rtog gi spros pa'i gra zur
NK102(ne)004:1489: las yongs su 'das pa'i thig le dpe mkha' dbyings
NK102(ne)004:1490: stong pa'i klong du 'od kyi thig le shar bas
NK102(ne)004:1491: mtshon pa ste / rdzogs chen gyi ston pa chen
NK102(ne)004:1492: po dga' rab rdo rje sku bltams pa'i tshe zhal
NK102(ne)004:1493: ton du mdzad par grags pa man ngag lung gi
NK102(ne)004:1494: rtsa ba rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che'i dgongs
NK102(ne)004:1495: mtshon pa ste / pa'ang / chos nyid kyi thig le /
NK102(ne)004:1497: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le /
NK102(ne)004:1498: ye shes chen po'i thig le /
NK102(ne)004:1499: kun tu bzang po'i thig le /
NK102(ne)004:1500: lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le bcas thig le drug gis bstan cing /
NK102(ne)004:1501: bsam gtan mig sgron las kyang thig le drug gi skor gsal bar bstan yod /
NK102(ne)004:1503: zhes chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs ji lta ba de la dbyings zhes pa'i brdas bsnyad cing /
NK102(ne)004:1504: de ni dper na snod bcud thams cad kyi gzhi
NK102(ne)004:1505: la mkha' dbyings zhes bya ba dang 'dra ba yin
NK102(ne)004:1507: gzung yul stong par gtan la phebs te gang zag gi bdag med pa mngon du 'gyur ba dang /
NK102(ne)004:1508: 'dzin pa rang bzhin ma grub pa gtan la phebs
NK102(ne)004:1509: pas chos kyi bdag med pa mngon du 'gyur ba
NK102(ne)004:1510: ste / bdag med gnyis stong gi chos dbyings chen
NK102(ne)004:1511: po ni thun mong theg pa'i lugs su grags che
NK102(ne)004:1512: ste / zhing / chos kun gyi gdod ma'i gshis
NK102(ne)004:1513: kyi gnas lugs dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'jug
NK102(ne)004:1514: pa las zung 'jug rdo rje'i skur bzhengs pa'i tshul
NK102(ne)004:1515: 'di ni sngags kyi lugs su grags na'ang /
NK102(ne)004:1516: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i skabs su
NK102(ne)004:1517: gzung 'dzin gnyis rtog gis phyes pa'i cha de gnas
NK102(ne)004:1519: snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang snang
NK102(ne)004:1520: tsam du gtan la phebs te rtogs pa mngon du
NK102(ne)004:1521: byed cing / lus rdul phran du dengs te phung po lhag med du sangs rgyas pa zhig gam /
NK102(ne)004:1522: gdod ma gzhi'i gnas lugs ye shes sum ldan gyi
NK102(ne)004:1523: bdag nyid nang gi dbyings de nyid phyi dbyings kyi
NK102(ne)004:1524: klong du thig le stong pa'i sgron mar shar ba
NK102(ne)004:1526: dbyings snang gcig tu bzlums shing 'ja' lus 'od kyi
NK102(ne)004:1527: skur grol ba bcas grol ba'i tshul khyad par can
NK102(ne)004:1528: gnyis dang 'brel ba'i dbyings kyi go tshul la'ang mi
NK102(ne)004:1529: 'dra ba'i khyad che bar yod pa'o////chos kyi 'phrul par
NK102(ne)004:1531: ma rnams tshe 'dir bde skyid dpal la rol //
NK102(ne)004:1532: 'chi khar nad gcod sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK102(ne)004:1533: phyi ma dag pa'i zhing du 'tshang rgya shog /
NK102(ne)004:1534: bka' dang bstan bcos gzhung lugs man ngag bcud //
NK102(ne)004:1535: bka' mar 'dus pas rin chen gter bzhin te //
NK102(ne)004:1536: bka' bzhin bsgrubs nus kun bzang sar phyin par //
NK102(ne)004:1537: bka' yi sdud po byang chub rgya mtshos smon //
NK102(ne)004:1538: zhes snga 'gyur bka' ma'i gzhung phyi mo dang rgyab
NK102(ne)004:1539: chos mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs te rtsis 'phrul
NK102(ne)004:1540: gyi par gzhi bzhengs skabs nges pa don gyi rdzogs
NK102(ne)004:1541: pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa mkhan chen bla ma
NK102(ne)004:1542: mun sel gyi gus slob tha ma'i yang tha chos
NK102(ne)004:1543: rdzogs chen du song yang gang zag rdzogs chen du
NK102(ne)004:1544: ma song bas / rang rgyud nyon mongs pa'i phung
NK102(ne)004:1545: pos non na'ang cha lugs lha chos ltar bcos pa'i
NK102(ne)004:1546: snyom las pa byang chub rgya mtshos rdzogs pa chen
NK102(ne)004:1547: po'i rnal 'byor pa chos rgyal nam mkha'i nor bu'i
